window.SHADOWING_DATA = {"interview":[{"id":1,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Okay, let’s kick things off.","literal_zh":"好吧，让我们开始吧。","audio":"audio/0001_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.126},{"id":2,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Can you tell us a little bit about yourself and what you do?","literal_zh":"你能告诉我们一点关于你自己的事情吗？","audio":"audio/0002_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.422},{"id":3,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Sure.","literal_zh":"当然","audio":"audio/0003_perrin.mp3","duration":1.91},{"id":4,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"My name is Perrin, and my husband is Jeff.","literal_zh":"我叫Perrin，我丈夫叫Jeff","audio":"audio/0004_perrin.mp3","duration":3.926},{"id":5,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We run a YouTube channel called Paired and Powered Up.","literal_zh":"我们经营一个名为Paired和Powered Up的YouTube频道.","audio":"audio/0005_perrin.mp3","duration":3.974},{"id":6,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"It is focused on home gym equipment reviews.","literal_zh":"重点是家庭体育器材审查。","audio":"audio/0006_perrin.mp3","duration":3.734},{"id":7,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"What makes our reviews a little different is that we test everything from two perspectives.","literal_zh":"使我们的评论稍有不同，就是我们从两个角度检验一切。","audio":"audio/0007_perrin.mp3","duration":5.654},{"id":8,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"I am 5'5\" and about 120 pounds.","literal_zh":"我身高5英尺5，体重120磅左右","audio":"audio/0008_perrin.mp3","duration":4.934},{"id":9,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Jeff is 5'11\" and about 200 pounds.","literal_zh":"Jeff身高5英尺11 体重约200磅","audio":"audio/0009_perrin.mp3","duration":4.862},{"id":10,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"So we can show how the same piece of equipment works for two very different body types.","literal_zh":"因此，我们可以显示同一件设备如何适用于两种非常不同的身体类型。","audio":"audio/0010_perrin.mp3","duration":5.798},{"id":11,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We both use every product we review.","literal_zh":"我们都使用我们审查的所有产品。","audio":"audio/0011_perrin.mp3","duration":3.398},{"id":12,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We usually test it for at least three weeks and work it into our normal workout routine.","literal_zh":"我们通常至少测试三个星期 然后把它做成正常的锻炼","audio":"audio/0012_perrin.mp3","duration":5.822},{"id":13,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"That way the review feels real, not just like a first impression.","literal_zh":"这样一来，评论感觉是真实的，而不仅仅是第一印象.","audio":"audio/0013_perrin.mp3","duration":4.886},{"id":14,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"After that, we put together a full review for our audience.","literal_zh":"之后，我们为观众整理了完整的评论.","audio":"audio/0014_perrin.mp3","duration":4.646},{"id":15,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We started the channel about a year and a half ago, and it has grown a lot since then.","literal_zh":"我们大约在一年半前开始这个频道，从那时起它发展了很多.","audio":"audio/0015_perrin.mp3","duration":5.726},{"id":16,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We are starting to review bigger pieces of equipment now, and JabX came up as something we would be interested in testing.","literal_zh":"我们开始审查更大的设备， JabX作为我们有兴趣测试的东西。","audio":"audio/0016_perrin.mp3","duration":7.574},{"id":17,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Nice.","literal_zh":"不错","audio":"audio/0017_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.19},{"id":18,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"And just so we understand the scale, how big is your audience right now?","literal_zh":"我们了解这个尺度 你的观众现在有多少人？","audio":"audio/0018_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.142},{"id":19,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We have about 2,600 subscribers on YouTube right now, and it is growing steadily.","literal_zh":"我们目前在YouTube上约有2600个订户，并且正在稳步增长。","audio":"audio/0019_perrin.mp3","duration":6.542},{"id":20,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Our Instagram following is smaller, but I would need to check the exact number.","literal_zh":"我们的Instagram跟随较小， 但我需要检查确切的数字。","audio":"audio/0020_perrin.mp3","duration":5.39},{"id":21,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Got it.","literal_zh":"明白吗？","audio":"audio/0021_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.126},{"id":22,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"Where in the U.S. are you based?","literal_zh":"你在美国在哪里？","audio":"audio/0022_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.366},{"id":23,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We are in New Hampshire, right on the border of Vermont and New Hampshire.","literal_zh":"我们在新罕布什尔州 就在佛蒙特州和新罕布什尔州的边境","audio":"audio/0023_perrin.mp3","duration":5.03},{"id":24,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"So we are up in New England.","literal_zh":"所以我们在新英格兰。","audio":"audio/0024_perrin.mp3","duration":2.846},{"id":25,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"访谈开场与频道背景","english":"We are in the Eastern time zone.","literal_zh":"我们在东部时区。","audio":"audio/0025_perrin.mp3","duration":3.014},{"id":26,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"I saw in the survey that boxing is not really part of your regular routine yet.","literal_zh":"我在调查中看到 拳击并不是你常规的一部分","audio":"audio/0026_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.646},{"id":27,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Is that fair?","literal_zh":"公平吗？","audio":"audio/0027_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.574},{"id":28,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Not as a regular routine.","literal_zh":"不是例行公事","audio":"audio/0028_perrin.mp3","duration":2.918},{"id":29,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"I have done some footwork and a few small boxing-style movements, but I have never trained in boxing consistently.","literal_zh":"我做了一些脚踏实地的工作和一些小的拳击风格的动作，但我从来没有一贯地训练拳击.","audio":"audio/0029_perrin.mp3","duration":7.31},{"id":30,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"My husband has not really done it either.","literal_zh":"我的丈夫也没有真正做到这一点。","audio":"audio/0030_perrin.mp3","duration":3.35},{"id":31,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"But I have always been interested in it.","literal_zh":"但我一直很感兴趣","audio":"audio/0031_perrin.mp3","duration":3.206},{"id":32,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"I know boxing is good cardio.","literal_zh":"我知道拳击是好心术。","audio":"audio/0032_perrin.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":33,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"It is also good for agility and coordination.","literal_zh":"这也有利于灵活和协调。","audio":"audio/0033_perrin.mp3","duration":3.878},{"id":34,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Another reason I am interested is personal.","literal_zh":"我感兴趣的另一个原因是个人原因。","audio":"audio/0034_perrin.mp3","duration":3.638},{"id":35,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Both of my parents had Parkinson's disease.","literal_zh":"我父母都得了帕金森氏症","audio":"audio/0035_perrin.mp3","duration":3.71},{"id":36,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Boxing is often recommended for people with Parkinson's because it can help with coordination and movement.","literal_zh":"拳击经常被推荐给有帕金森症的人，因为它可以帮助协调和运动.","audio":"audio/0036_perrin.mp3","duration":6.734},{"id":37,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"So if JabX could also be positioned as a tool for people with Parkinson's, that would be a very strong angle for me.","literal_zh":"所以，如果JabX也可以被定位为 帕金森症患者的工具， 那对我来说是一个非常强烈的角度。","audio":"audio/0037_perrin.mp3","duration":7.598},{"id":38,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"My parents have both passed away, and they never really had the chance to get into boxing.","literal_zh":"我的父母都去世了， 他们从来没有真正的机会 进入拳击。","audio":"audio/0038_perrin.mp3","duration":6.038},{"id":39,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"But if they had had something like JabX at home and could have used it often, I think it would have been a great tool for them.","literal_zh":"但如果他们在家里有类似JabX的东西，并且可以经常使用，我想这对他们来说是一个伟大的工具.","audio":"audio/0039_perrin.mp3","duration":7.214},{"id":40,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"That is actually a super helpful angle.","literal_zh":"这实际上是一个超级有益的角度。","audio":"audio/0040_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.75},{"id":41,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Can you walk us through why boxing is useful for people with Parkinson's?","literal_zh":"你能告诉我们为什么 拳击对帕金森的人有用吗？","audio":"audio/0041_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.238},{"id":42,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Parkinson's is a neurological disease.","literal_zh":"帕金森氏症是一种神经病.","audio":"audio/0042_perrin.mp3","duration":3.566},{"id":43,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"It affects the nervous system and the body's ability to control movement.","literal_zh":"它影响神经系统和身体控制运动的能力.","audio":"audio/0043_perrin.mp3","duration":4.982},{"id":44,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Boxing works on coordination, and coordination is one of the hardest things for people with Parkinson's.","literal_zh":"拳击工作在协调方面，而协调是帕金森(英语:Parkinson)的人最难处理的事情之一.","audio":"audio/0044_perrin.mp3","duration":6.998},{"id":45,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"You are using your hands, your feet, your eyes and your timing all at once.","literal_zh":"你用手、脚、眼睛和时间","audio":"audio/0045_perrin.mp3","duration":5.75},{"id":46,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"That kind of training can help activate those movement patterns.","literal_zh":"这种培训可以帮助激活这些运动模式。","audio":"audio/0046_perrin.mp3","duration":4.622},{"id":47,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"I do not know all the research in detail, but I know boxing is commonly encouraged for Parkinson's patients.","literal_zh":"我不知道所有的详细研究， 但我知道拳击是帕金森的病人普遍鼓励的。","audio":"audio/0047_perrin.mp3","duration":7.214},{"id":48,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Michael J.","literal_zh":"迈克尔·J.","audio":"audio/0048_perrin.mp3","duration":2.222},{"id":49,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"Fox, the actor, also has a foundation for Parkinson's research, and they have a lot of information on this topic.","literal_zh":"演员福克斯也为帕金森的研究打下了基础，他们对这个话题有不少信息.","audio":"audio/0049_perrin.mp3","duration":8.006},{"id":50,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"For me, the key point is access.","literal_zh":"对我来说，关键是进入。","audio":"audio/0050_perrin.mp3","duration":3.638},{"id":51,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"A lot of people may not have a place nearby where they can do boxing.","literal_zh":"很多人可能在附近没有可以进行拳击的地方.","audio":"audio/0051_perrin.mp3","duration":4.958},{"id":52,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"拳击与帕金森病的推广角度","english":"If they can do it safely at home, that could make a big difference.","literal_zh":"如果他们能在家里安全地做，那会有很大的不同。","audio":"audio/0052_perrin.mp3","duration":4.814},{"id":53,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"What about your area?","literal_zh":"那你的地盘呢？","audio":"audio/0053_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.934},{"id":54,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"Is boxing something people around you are into, or is it still pretty niche?","literal_zh":"拳击是你周围的人喜欢的东西， 还是它仍然相当适合？","audio":"audio/0054_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.742},{"id":55,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"Boxing is one of those things that can intimidate people, but it also gets them excited.","literal_zh":"拳击是一种能吓人的东西，但也让他们兴奋.","audio":"audio/0055_perrin.mp3","duration":6.038},{"id":56,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"We live in a rural area, so there are not many places nearby where people can do it.","literal_zh":"我们生活在一个农村地区，所以附近没有多少地方是人们可以做到的.","audio":"audio/0056_perrin.mp3","duration":5.798},{"id":57,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"That is a big reason we built a home gym.","literal_zh":"那是我们建家用健身房的一个大原因","audio":"audio/0057_perrin.mp3","duration":3.614},{"id":58,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"We would have to drive about 20 minutes to get to a gym.","literal_zh":"我们得开车20分钟才能到健身房","audio":"audio/0058_perrin.mp3","duration":4.262},{"id":59,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"At the end of a long day, that is not always something you want to do.","literal_zh":"在漫长的一天结束时，这并不总是你想做的事情。","audio":"audio/0059_perrin.mp3","duration":4.862},{"id":60,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"You do not want to drive 20 minutes there, work out for an hour, and then drive 20 minutes back.","literal_zh":"你不想在那里开车20分钟， 工作一个小时，然后开车20分钟回来。","audio":"audio/0060_perrin.mp3","duration":6.734},{"id":61,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"So we are big believers in at-home fitness.","literal_zh":"所以我们是在家里健身的大信徒。","audio":"audio/0061_perrin.mp3","duration":3.782},{"id":62,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"A product like JabX could make boxing easier to bring into a home routine.","literal_zh":"像JabX这样的产品可以让拳击更容易带入家常便饭.","audio":"audio/0062_perrin.mp3","duration":5.438},{"id":63,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"The variety is also important.","literal_zh":"品种也很重要。","audio":"audio/0063_perrin.mp3","duration":3.11},{"id":64,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"People get bored doing the same workout every day.","literal_zh":"人们每天都会厌倦同样的锻炼","audio":"audio/0064_perrin.mp3","duration":3.926},{"id":65,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"If they can add boxing into the mix, it keeps things fresh.","literal_zh":"如果他们能把拳击加进混音中，它能保持事物新鲜.","audio":"audio/0065_perrin.mp3","duration":4.622},{"id":66,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"It is not just a bag hanging from the ceiling.","literal_zh":"这不仅仅是吊在天花板上的袋子。","audio":"audio/0066_perrin.mp3","duration":3.662},{"id":67,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"居家健身场景与拳击普及度","english":"If the product gives guidance and helps you through the workout, that is much more appealing.","literal_zh":"如果产品能指导你 帮助你通过锻炼，那就更有吸引力了。","audio":"audio/0067_perrin.mp3","duration":5.75},{"id":68,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"When it comes to training, are you more of a solo-workout person, or do you and your husband like doing it together?","literal_zh":"在训练方面，你比较喜欢独修，还是你和你丈夫喜欢一起做？","audio":"audio/0068_interviewer.mp3","duration":6.326},{"id":69,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We do both.","literal_zh":"我们都是","audio":"audio/0069_perrin.mp3","duration":2.222},{"id":70,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"My husband is a UPS driver, so his schedule is not always predictable.","literal_zh":"我丈夫是UPS司机，所以他的行程并非总能预测.","audio":"audio/0070_perrin.mp3","duration":5.582},{"id":71,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Some days we can work out together.","literal_zh":"有时候我们可以一起工作","audio":"audio/0071_perrin.mp3","duration":3.278},{"id":72,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Some days we cannot.","literal_zh":"有时候，我们不能。","audio":"audio/0072_perrin.mp3","duration":2.63},{"id":73,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"I also have a friend who comes over and works out with me in the home gym.","literal_zh":"我也有个朋友过来 跟我在健身房工作","audio":"audio/0073_perrin.mp3","duration":4.91},{"id":74,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"So it depends on the day.","literal_zh":"故视日.","audio":"audio/0074_perrin.mp3","duration":2.774},{"id":75,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Sometimes Jeff and I are in the same room, but we are doing different workouts or using different equipment.","literal_zh":"有时Jeff和我在同一间房 但我们在做不同的锻炼 或者使用不同的设备","audio":"audio/0075_perrin.mp3","duration":6.782},{"id":76,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Other times we do the same workout together.","literal_zh":"其他时候我们一起做同样的锻炼。","audio":"audio/0076_perrin.mp3","duration":3.662},{"id":77,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We like switching things up so it does not get boring.","literal_zh":"我们喜欢换东西 这样才不会无聊","audio":"audio/0077_perrin.mp3","duration":4.022},{"id":78,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Have you ever tried BodyCombat or those boxing-style online classes at home?","literal_zh":"你试过拳击或那些拳击式的在线课程吗？","audio":"audio/0078_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.79},{"id":79,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We do some aerobic work, but I probably do more of that than Jeff.","literal_zh":"我们做一些有氧工作 但我可能做的比Jeff多","audio":"audio/0079_perrin.mp3","duration":5.078},{"id":80,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"He is more focused on building muscle right now.","literal_zh":"他现在更注重肌肉建设","audio":"audio/0080_perrin.mp3","duration":3.71},{"id":81,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"I like to include more cardio.","literal_zh":"我喜欢包括更多的心肌。","audio":"audio/0081_perrin.mp3","duration":3.11},{"id":82,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"That said, he is open to different types of cardio if they are useful.","literal_zh":"尽管如此，他愿意接受不同类型的心电图，如果它们有用的话。","audio":"audio/0082_perrin.mp3","duration":5.078},{"id":83,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"If something works on mobility, dexterity or hand-eye coordination, he is more interested in it.","literal_zh":"如果有东西在机动性，机敏性或手眼协调上起作用，他对此更感兴趣.","audio":"audio/0083_perrin.mp3","duration":6.878},{"id":84,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"He wants cardio that still feels like it is helping his overall fitness.","literal_zh":"他想要的心肺 仍然觉得这能帮助他身体健康","audio":"audio/0084_perrin.mp3","duration":5.006},{"id":85,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"What does a normal workout week look like for you?","literal_zh":"正常的锻炼周对你来说是什么样子？","audio":"audio/0085_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.038},{"id":86,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We work out almost every day.","literal_zh":"我们几乎每天都工作","audio":"audio/0086_perrin.mp3","duration":2.966},{"id":87,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Jeff lifts five days a week.","literal_zh":"Jeff每周举5天","audio":"audio/0087_perrin.mp3","duration":3.062},{"id":88,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"I lift three days a week, sometimes four.","literal_zh":"我每周抬三天，有时四天","audio":"audio/0088_perrin.mp3","duration":3.878},{"id":89,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"I also try to add cardio two or three days a week.","literal_zh":"我还试着每周增加两三天的心跳。","audio":"audio/0089_perrin.mp3","duration":4.358},{"id":90,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Jeff uses the treadmill for hiking sometimes.","literal_zh":"Jeff有时会用跑步车徒步旅行","audio":"audio/0090_perrin.mp3","duration":3.902},{"id":91,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Even when we are not lifting, we are usually doing some type of fitness.","literal_zh":"即使我们没有升起，我们通常也在做某种健身。","audio":"audio/0091_perrin.mp3","duration":5.198},{"id":92,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We may take one day off.","literal_zh":"我们可以休息一天","audio":"audio/0092_perrin.mp3","duration":2.846},{"id":93,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We usually work out in the evening.","literal_zh":"我们通常晚上一起工作","audio":"audio/0093_perrin.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":94,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"We are not really morning people.","literal_zh":"我们不是真的早上的人。","audio":"audio/0094_perrin.mp3","duration":3.014},{"id":95,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"单人/双人训练与日常习惯","english":"Most of our workouts are around an hour.","literal_zh":"我们大部分的锻炼时间都在一小时左右","audio":"audio/0095_perrin.mp3","duration":3.47},{"id":96,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Besides the treadmill, what else do you use for cardio at home?","literal_zh":"除了跑步车，你在家里还用什么做心跳？","audio":"audio/0096_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.806},{"id":97,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Anything like a Peloton bike?","literal_zh":"像是皮洛顿自行车吗？","audio":"audio/0097_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.342},{"id":98,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"We used to have a Peloton bike, but we did not use it much.","literal_zh":"我们曾经有一辆皮洛顿自行车，但是没有怎么使用.","audio":"audio/0098_perrin.mp3","duration":4.646},{"id":99,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"It was uncomfortable, and it was mostly lower-body work.","literal_zh":"感觉很不舒服，而且大多是下体工作.","audio":"audio/0099_perrin.mp3","duration":4.526},{"id":100,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"I prefer equipment that gives more full-body engagement.","literal_zh":"我更喜欢更能全身心投入的设备","audio":"audio/0100_perrin.mp3","duration":4.286},{"id":101,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"We also had a rower for a while, but we still used the treadmill more than anything else.","literal_zh":"我们还有一个划船的一段时间， 但我们仍然使用 跑步机比任何其他。","audio":"audio/0101_perrin.mp3","duration":5.966},{"id":102,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Right now, we are reviewing some cardio-focused equipment.","literal_zh":"现在，我们正在审查一些以心肺为重点的设备。","audio":"audio/0102_perrin.mp3","duration":4.694},{"id":103,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"We have used Concept2 products, like the SkiErg, StrengthErg and RowErg.","literal_zh":"我们使用了Concept2产品，如SkiErg，FriendErg和RowErg.","audio":"audio/0103_perrin.mp3","duration":5.798},{"id":104,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"We also have a machine that feels like a mix between a rower and an elliptical because it uses both the hands and feet.","literal_zh":"我们还有一台机器，它感觉像划船和椭圆形的混合体，因为它同时使用手和脚.","audio":"audio/0104_perrin.mp3","duration":7.358},{"id":105,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"The biggest issue is space.","literal_zh":"最大的问题是空间。","audio":"audio/0105_perrin.mp3","duration":2.918},{"id":106,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"We cannot keep everything we review.","literal_zh":"我们不能保留我们审查的一切。","audio":"audio/0106_perrin.mp3","duration":3.182},{"id":107,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"If we really like something and know we will use it all the time, we keep it.","literal_zh":"如果我们真的喜欢的东西，知道我们会一直使用它，我们保留它。","audio":"audio/0107_perrin.mp3","duration":5.318},{"id":108,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Otherwise, we usually sell it after the review.","literal_zh":"否则，我们通常在审查后出售。","audio":"audio/0108_perrin.mp3","duration":3.998},{"id":109,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"JabX is about 16 feet long, so it is not tiny.","literal_zh":"JabX长约16英尺，所以并不小.","audio":"audio/0109_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.854},{"id":110,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"In your setup, would that be realistic?","literal_zh":"在你的设定， 这是现实吗？","audio":"audio/0110_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.798},{"id":111,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"We actually have two gym spaces now.","literal_zh":"我们现在有两个健身房","audio":"audio/0111_perrin.mp3","duration":3.47},{"id":112,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"One is in a living room that we converted into a gym.","literal_zh":"一个在客厅里 我们把一个健身房改造了","audio":"audio/0112_perrin.mp3","duration":4.094},{"id":113,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"The other is in our garage, which we recently turned into a second gym space.","literal_zh":"另一个是在我们的车库， 我们最近变成了第二个健身房。","audio":"audio/0113_perrin.mp3","duration":5.534},{"id":114,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"So we would have a couple of options.","literal_zh":"所以我们有几种选择。","audio":"audio/0114_perrin.mp3","duration":3.23},{"id":115,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"The garage gym would probably be the best place for JabX.","literal_zh":"车库健身房可能是最好的 JabX。","audio":"audio/0115_perrin.mp3","duration":4.598},{"id":116,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Would an easy-move design matter to you?","literal_zh":"一个容易移动的设计对你很重要吗？","audio":"audio/0116_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.702},{"id":117,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Like wheels, so you can roll it out and tuck it away?","literal_zh":"像轮子一样，这样你就可以把它卷起来，把它盖起来？","audio":"audio/0117_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.23},{"id":118,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Absolutely.","literal_zh":"当然","audio":"audio/0118_perrin.mp3","duration":2.222},{"id":119,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"If it did not have wheels, I would probably add them.","literal_zh":"如果它没有轮子，我可能会加起来。","audio":"audio/0119_perrin.mp3","duration":4.142},{"id":120,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"In a home gym, being able to move equipment is really important.","literal_zh":"在家庭体育馆里，能够移动设备非常重要。","audio":"audio/0120_perrin.mp3","duration":4.958},{"id":121,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"If you can store it in a corner and pull it out when you need it, that helps a lot.","literal_zh":"如果你可以把它储存在角落里，并在你需要的时候把它拔出来，那会很有帮助.","audio":"audio/0121_perrin.mp3","duration":5.534},{"id":122,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Especially if the space is smaller.","literal_zh":"特别是如果空间较小。","audio":"audio/0122_perrin.mp3","duration":3.254},{"id":123,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"现有器械、空间与移动性需求","english":"Portability is a big deal.","literal_zh":"便携是大事.","audio":"audio/0123_perrin.mp3","duration":2.942},{"id":124,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"How do you usually plan your workouts?","literal_zh":"你平时是怎么安排运动的？","audio":"audio/0124_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.606},{"id":125,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Are you following your own plan, or does someone build it for you?","literal_zh":"你是在遵循你自己的计划 还是有人帮你建的？","audio":"audio/0125_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.214},{"id":126,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"I have a virtual trainer who builds my workouts for me.","literal_zh":"我有个虚拟的教练 帮我做锻炼","audio":"audio/0126_perrin.mp3","duration":4.07},{"id":127,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"He bases them on what I am trying to work on, and he also keeps me motivated.","literal_zh":"他以我努力的工作为基础，他也保持我的积极性。","audio":"audio/0127_perrin.mp3","duration":5.462},{"id":128,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"My husband is certified, so he writes his own workouts.","literal_zh":"我丈夫有认证，所以他写自己的锻炼。","audio":"audio/0128_perrin.mp3","duration":4.502},{"id":129,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"He usually does upper-body and lower-body splits.","literal_zh":"他通常进行上体和下体分裂.","audio":"audio/0129_perrin.mp3","duration":4.142},{"id":130,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"His workouts are more targeted.","literal_zh":"他的锻炼更具有针对性.","audio":"audio/0130_perrin.mp3","duration":2.942},{"id":131,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Mine are more full-body.","literal_zh":"我的身体更满满","audio":"audio/0131_perrin.mp3","duration":2.654},{"id":132,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"I do three full-body workouts a week.","literal_zh":"我每周做三次全身运动","audio":"audio/0132_perrin.mp3","duration":3.422},{"id":133,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"For cardio, I usually do whatever I am interested in at the time.","literal_zh":"对于心律，我通常做任何我感兴趣的时候。","audio":"audio/0133_perrin.mp3","duration":4.958},{"id":134,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Some days I run.","literal_zh":"有时候我跑。","audio":"audio/0134_perrin.mp3","duration":2.462},{"id":135,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Some days I walk.","literal_zh":"有时候我走路","audio":"audio/0135_perrin.mp3","duration":2.51},{"id":136,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Some days I hike.","literal_zh":"有时候我走了。","audio":"audio/0136_perrin.mp3","duration":2.534},{"id":137,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"We also have a Tonal, so I use some of its cardio features from time to time.","literal_zh":"我们还有一个Tonal， 所以我不时使用它的一些心肺功能。","audio":"audio/0137_perrin.mp3","duration":5.558},{"id":138,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"I usually like to warm up with about a 10-minute walk before I lift.","literal_zh":"我通常喜欢在升起前用10分钟的步行来取暖.","audio":"audio/0138_perrin.mp3","duration":5.054},{"id":139,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Jeff does something similar.","literal_zh":"Jeff做类似的事情。","audio":"audio/0139_perrin.mp3","duration":2.87},{"id":140,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Our strength training is hypertrophy-focused.","literal_zh":"我们的实力训练是超营养的","audio":"audio/0140_perrin.mp3","duration":3.878},{"id":141,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"So we do sets with rest periods in between.","literal_zh":"因此，我们确实安排了休息时间。","audio":"audio/0141_perrin.mp3","duration":3.854},{"id":142,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"The rest might be one, two or three minutes, depending on the movement and what we are trying to build.","literal_zh":"其余的可能是一、二或三分钟，这取决于我们的行动和我们试图建设的东西。","audio":"audio/0142_perrin.mp3","duration":7.046},{"id":143,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"What does personal training usually cost, at least from what you have seen?","literal_zh":"个人培训通常需要多少费用，至少从你所看到的情况来看？","audio":"audio/0143_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.238},{"id":144,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"It really depends on the setup.","literal_zh":"这真的取决于设置。","audio":"audio/0144_perrin.mp3","duration":2.966},{"id":145,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"If you go to a gym, a trainer is often around $75 to $100 an hour.","literal_zh":"如果你去健身房，一个教练经常是每小时75到100美元左右.","audio":"audio/0145_perrin.mp3","duration":6.71},{"id":146,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"If you train with them two or three times a week, that gets expensive quickly.","literal_zh":"如果你每周和他们一起训练两三次，那会很快变得昂贵.","audio":"audio/0146_perrin.mp3","duration":5.534},{"id":147,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"There are also group-style online programs.","literal_zh":"也有团体式在线程序.","audio":"audio/0147_perrin.mp3","duration":3.686},{"id":148,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"A trainer builds one program, and everyone who signs up follows it.","literal_zh":"训练员会建立一套程序 每一个签字的人都会遵守","audio":"audio/0148_perrin.mp3","duration":5.006},{"id":149,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"That might cost around $40 a month.","literal_zh":"这可能需要大约每月40美元。","audio":"audio/0149_perrin.mp3","duration":3.758},{"id":150,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"It is not personalized, but it gives you structure.","literal_zh":"它不是个性化的，但它给了你结构。","audio":"audio/0150_perrin.mp3","duration":4.094},{"id":151,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"My trainer is one-on-one.","literal_zh":"我的教练是一对一。","audio":"audio/0151_perrin.mp3","duration":2.798},{"id":152,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"He builds the program around me.","literal_zh":"他围绕我构建了程序。","audio":"audio/0152_perrin.mp3","duration":2.99},{"id":153,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"We communicate almost every day.","literal_zh":"我们几乎每天都在沟通","audio":"audio/0153_perrin.mp3","duration":3.302},{"id":154,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"I send him videos of my form so he can check whether I am doing the movements correctly.","literal_zh":"我给他发了我表格的视频 这样他就可以检查我是否正确行动了","audio":"audio/0154_perrin.mp3","duration":5.846},{"id":155,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"He also helps with meal planning.","literal_zh":"他还帮助制定膳食计划.","audio":"audio/0155_perrin.mp3","duration":3.11},{"id":156,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"It is all virtual.","literal_zh":"这都是虚拟的。","audio":"audio/0156_perrin.mp3","duration":2.462},{"id":157,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"We use Zoom, texting and things like that.","literal_zh":"我们使用Zoom，发短信和类似的东西。","audio":"audio/0157_perrin.mp3","duration":4.07},{"id":158,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"He costs around $400 a month, but it is a much more personal relationship.","literal_zh":"他每月花费约400美元，但这更是个人关系.","audio":"audio/0158_perrin.mp3","duration":6.302},{"id":159,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Are you seeing people use AI for workout plans now?","literal_zh":"你看见有人用人工智能做健身计划了吗？","audio":"audio/0159_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.494},{"id":160,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Definitely.","literal_zh":"当然","audio":"audio/0160_perrin.mp3","duration":2.15},{"id":161,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"A lot of people use ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini or other AI tools to build workouts.","literal_zh":"很多人使用ChatGPT，克劳德，双子座或其他AI工具来构建健身.","audio":"audio/0161_perrin.mp3","duration":6.902},{"id":162,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"They tell the AI their goal, how often they can work out and how much time they have.","literal_zh":"他们告诉AI他们的目标，他们能工作多久，还有多少时间.","audio":"audio/0162_perrin.mp3","duration":5.678},{"id":163,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"训练计划、私教模式与费用","english":"Then it gives them a plan.","literal_zh":"那就给他们一个计划","audio":"audio/0163_perrin.mp3","duration":2.678},{"id":164,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"That is exactly the direction we are thinking about for JabX.","literal_zh":"这就是我们为JabX考虑的方向。","audio":"audio/0164_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.022},{"id":165,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"The dream is to give people some of that personal-trainer feel, but built into the product.","literal_zh":"梦想是给人们一些 个人教练的感觉， 但是在产品中。","audio":"audio/0165_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.078},{"id":166,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"For example, JabX could track heart rate, punching speed and punching power through sensors.","literal_zh":"例如，JabX可以通过传感器跟踪心率，冲锋速度和冲锋功率.","audio":"audio/0166_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.75},{"id":167,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"The way we are thinking about it is pretty simple.","literal_zh":"我们的想法很简单。","audio":"audio/0167_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.062},{"id":168,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"There are three pieces to it.","literal_zh":"有三块.","audio":"audio/0168_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.15},{"id":169,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"First, data collection.","literal_zh":"一，数据采集.","audio":"audio/0169_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.03},{"id":170,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"The data could come from an app connected to Apple Watch, Samsung Watch or other wearables.","literal_zh":"数据可能来自与苹果卫视，三星卫视或其他可穿戴设备连接的应用程序.","audio":"audio/0170_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.582},{"id":171,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"It could also come from JabX sensors that track heart rate, punching speed, power and movement quality.","literal_zh":"也可以来自跟踪心率，拳击速度，功率和运动质量的JabX传感器.","audio":"audio/0171_interviewer.mp3","duration":6.542},{"id":172,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"Second is analysis.","literal_zh":"二是分析.","audio":"audio/0172_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.126},{"id":173,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"The system could look at movement correction, workout performance and heart rate zones.","literal_zh":"该系统可以研究运动矫正、锻炼性能和心率区。","audio":"audio/0173_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.838},{"id":174,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"Third is content generation.","literal_zh":"第三是内容生成.","audio":"audio/0174_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.39},{"id":175,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"Based on the user's data, it could create a 30-minute workout or even a longer plan, like a one-month program.","literal_zh":"根据用户的数据，它可以创建30分钟的锻炼甚至更长的计划，比如一个一个月的程序.","audio":"audio/0175_interviewer.mp3","duration":6.782},{"id":176,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"So it would create workouts that are customized to the person, based on their data and their level?","literal_zh":"这样它就能根据个人的数据和水平，创造适合个人的健身方案？","audio":"audio/0176_perrin.mp3","duration":6.158},{"id":177,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"Exactly.","literal_zh":"没错","audio":"audio/0177_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.502},{"id":178,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"We also want to use a camera for form correction, so the system can actually see how the user is moving.","literal_zh":"我们还想用相机进行形式校正，因此系统可以实际看到用户是如何移动的.","audio":"audio/0178_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.846},{"id":179,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"That is helpful.","literal_zh":"这很有帮助。","audio":"audio/0179_perrin.mp3","duration":2.342},{"id":180,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"If it can correct form and movement in real time, that is a strong feature.","literal_zh":"如果它能够实时纠正形式和运动，这是一个很强的特点。","audio":"audio/0180_perrin.mp3","duration":5.342},{"id":181,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"If the user is too slow, or their form is off, the system should tell them.","literal_zh":"如果用户速度太慢，或者其形式被关闭，系统应该告诉他们.","audio":"audio/0181_perrin.mp3","duration":5.51},{"id":182,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"It could also adjust to the user's height, so the pad positions and target path fit the person better during training.","literal_zh":"它还可以适应用户的高度，因此垫位和瞄准路径在训练期间更适合人.","audio":"audio/0182_interviewer.mp3","duration":6.782},{"id":183,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"That is really useful.","literal_zh":"这真的有用。","audio":"audio/0183_perrin.mp3","duration":2.678},{"id":184,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"It sounds like you are trying to put a lot of the personal-trainer experience into the machine.","literal_zh":"听起来你试图把很多 个人教练的经验投入机器。","audio":"audio/0184_perrin.mp3","duration":5.726},{"id":185,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"And because regular training can get boring fast, we also want to build in games, especially for beginners.","literal_zh":"并且由于常规训练可以变得无聊快，我们也想在游戏中建设，特别是初学者.","audio":"audio/0185_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.822},{"id":186,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"That makes sense.","literal_zh":"这有道理。","audio":"audio/0186_perrin.mp3","duration":2.462},{"id":187,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"Games can make boxing more competitive and more fun.","literal_zh":"游戏可以让拳击更具竞争力和乐趣.","audio":"audio/0187_perrin.mp3","duration":4.094},{"id":188,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练功能设想","english":"A lot of people are motivated by that.","literal_zh":"很多人都为此而奋斗.","audio":"audio/0188_perrin.mp3","duration":3.518},{"id":189,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"With your trainer, do you usually set a specific goal together?","literal_zh":"与你的教练， 你通常设置一个特定的目标在一起？","audio":"audio/0189_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.83},{"id":190,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"Like losing weight, building muscle or hitting a target by a certain date?","literal_zh":"比如减肥，建立肌肉或者在某个日期前击中目标？","audio":"audio/0190_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.31},{"id":191,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I do not really have a short-term goal like that.","literal_zh":"我并没有这样的短期目标。","audio":"audio/0191_perrin.mp3","duration":3.686},{"id":192,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I keep working with him because he motivates me and because he handles the planning.","literal_zh":"我一直和他合作 因为他激励我 并且他负责计划","audio":"audio/0192_perrin.mp3","duration":5.366},{"id":193,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I know a lot of the exercises.","literal_zh":"我知道很多练习。","audio":"audio/0193_perrin.mp3","duration":3.23},{"id":194,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I probably could figure it out myself.","literal_zh":"我也许能自己弄明白","audio":"audio/0194_perrin.mp3","duration":3.422},{"id":195,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"But I do not want to think about programming.","literal_zh":"但我不想考虑编程。","audio":"audio/0195_perrin.mp3","duration":3.446},{"id":196,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I already organize so much in the rest of my life.","literal_zh":"我已经组织这么多 在我的生活的余生。","audio":"audio/0196_perrin.mp3","duration":4.286},{"id":197,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"It is nice to have someone else build the plan so I can just show up and do it.","literal_zh":"让别人来做这个计划是件好事 这样我就可以亲自来做","audio":"audio/0197_perrin.mp3","duration":5.174},{"id":198,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"My main goal right now is building muscle.","literal_zh":"我现在的主要目标是建立肌肉。","audio":"audio/0198_perrin.mp3","duration":3.686},{"id":199,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I lost a lot of body fat over the last year, and now I want to build muscle.","literal_zh":"去年我失去了很多身体脂肪， 现在我想建立肌肉。","audio":"audio/0199_perrin.mp3","duration":5.582},{"id":200,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"That takes time.","literal_zh":"这需要时间。","audio":"audio/0200_perrin.mp3","duration":2.366},{"id":201,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"It does not happen overnight.","literal_zh":"它不会一夜之间发生。","audio":"audio/0201_perrin.mp3","duration":2.918},{"id":202,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"Right now, I am focused on eating enough calories and enough protein.","literal_zh":"现在，我专注于 吃足够的卡路里和足够的蛋白质。","audio":"audio/0202_perrin.mp3","duration":5.246},{"id":203,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"You cannot build muscle without that.","literal_zh":"没有它，你无法建立肌肉。","audio":"audio/0203_perrin.mp3","duration":3.206},{"id":204,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I also need balance.","literal_zh":"我还需要平衡","audio":"audio/0204_perrin.mp3","duration":2.678},{"id":205,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I need to balance strength training, cardio, other exercise and nutrition.","literal_zh":"我需要平衡力量训练，心肺，其他运动和营养.","audio":"audio/0205_perrin.mp3","duration":5.798},{"id":206,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"Eating is a huge part of being healthy.","literal_zh":"饮食是健康的一大部分.","audio":"audio/0206_perrin.mp3","duration":3.47},{"id":207,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"What you put into your body affects what you can do physically.","literal_zh":"你放进身体里会影响你的身体","audio":"audio/0207_perrin.mp3","duration":4.382},{"id":208,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I also need to make sure I am not doing so much cardio that it interferes with muscle building.","literal_zh":"我还得确保我没有做太多心肺病 以致于会妨碍肌肉建设","audio":"audio/0208_perrin.mp3","duration":6.11},{"id":209,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"If you do not mind me asking, how old are you?","literal_zh":"如果你不介意我问，你多大了？","audio":"audio/0209_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.966},{"id":210,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I am 48, and my husband is 53.","literal_zh":"我48岁，我丈夫53岁","audio":"audio/0210_perrin.mp3","duration":4.118},{"id":211,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"Do your kids work out too?","literal_zh":"你的孩子也会工作吗？","audio":"audio/0211_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.126},{"id":212,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"We have two sons.","literal_zh":"我们有两个儿子。","audio":"audio/0212_perrin.mp3","duration":2.558},{"id":213,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"One is 23, and one is 20.","literal_zh":"一个是23，一个是20。","audio":"audio/0213_perrin.mp3","duration":3.734},{"id":214,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"They both use our gym.","literal_zh":"他们都使用我们的健身房。","audio":"audio/0214_perrin.mp3","duration":2.678},{"id":215,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"My older son usually works out with my husband.","literal_zh":"我大儿子通常跟我丈夫一起工作","audio":"audio/0215_perrin.mp3","duration":3.974},{"id":216,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"My younger son likes to work out by himself because he does not like people watching him.","literal_zh":"我小儿子喜欢一个人工作 因为他不喜欢别人看他","audio":"audio/0216_perrin.mp3","duration":5.822},{"id":217,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"I think both of them would like the boxing product.","literal_zh":"我想他们俩都喜欢拳击产品","audio":"audio/0217_perrin.mp3","duration":3.734},{"id":218,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"My husband and my younger son are both very competitive.","literal_zh":"我丈夫和我小儿子都非常有竞争力","audio":"audio/0218_perrin.mp3","duration":4.502},{"id":219,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"个人训练目标与饮食平衡","english":"If JabX had a game mode where they could compete against each other, they would enjoy that.","literal_zh":"如果JabX有一个可以互相竞争的游戏模式，他们会享受这个.","audio":"audio/0219_perrin.mp3","duration":5.894},{"id":220,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"Be honest.","literal_zh":"老实说","audio":"audio/0220_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.478},{"id":221,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"Does indoor cardio ever get boring for you?","literal_zh":"室内心电图有没有让你觉得无聊？","audio":"audio/0221_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.966},{"id":222,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"Yes.","literal_zh":"对","audio":"audio/0222_perrin.mp3","duration":1.958},{"id":223,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"I usually watch cooking shows on the treadmill because treadmill cardio can get boring.","literal_zh":"我通常在跑步机上看烹饪节目 因为跑步机心跳会变得无聊","audio":"audio/0223_perrin.mp3","duration":5.774},{"id":224,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"I cannot just get on the treadmill and stare forward.","literal_zh":"我不能只上跑步机 向前看","audio":"audio/0224_perrin.mp3","duration":3.974},{"id":225,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"I need something to keep me engaged.","literal_zh":"我需要一些东西 保持我的订婚。","audio":"audio/0225_perrin.mp3","duration":3.254},{"id":226,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"Outside is different.","literal_zh":"外面不一样","audio":"audio/0226_perrin.mp3","duration":2.534},{"id":227,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"We live in a beautiful part of the country, so outdoor cardio feels better.","literal_zh":"我们生活在一个美丽的地方， 户外的心跳感觉更好。","audio":"audio/0227_perrin.mp3","duration":5.366},{"id":228,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"I can listen to music or an audiobook.","literal_zh":"我可以听音乐或听录音","audio":"audio/0228_perrin.mp3","duration":3.518},{"id":229,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"But indoors, you are just in one place.","literal_zh":"但是，室内，你只是在一个地方。","audio":"audio/0229_perrin.mp3","duration":3.806},{"id":230,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"室内有氧训练的无聊感","english":"If the treadmill has a screen, I might watch Netflix or something similar.","literal_zh":"如果跑步机有屏幕 我可能会看Netflix之类的","audio":"audio/0230_perrin.mp3","duration":5.246},{"id":231,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Let me show you how the JabX hardware works.","literal_zh":"让我告诉你JabX硬件是如何工作的","audio":"audio/0231_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":232,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"This is still a prototype, so think of it as the concept version.","literal_zh":"这仍然是一个原型，所以把它当作概念版本.","audio":"audio/0232_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.902},{"id":233,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"It has pads on the front and sides, including upper pads and stomach-level pads.","literal_zh":"它在正面和侧面都有垫，包括上垫和胃层垫.","audio":"audio/0233_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.366},{"id":234,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"There are lights inside the pads, and sensors can detect how hard the user punches.","literal_zh":"垫子内部有灯光，传感器可以探测到用户的拳击有多难.","audio":"audio/0234_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.222},{"id":235,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"There is also a large screen for classes, games and other content.","literal_zh":"还有一个大型屏幕，用于课堂，游戏和其他内容.","audio":"audio/0235_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.43},{"id":236,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"On the sides, there are two moving arms.","literal_zh":"侧面有两只移动的手臂.","audio":"audio/0236_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.726},{"id":237,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"They are designed to make it feel more like training with a real boxing coach.","literal_zh":"他们设计它是为了让感觉更像是训练 一个真正的拳击教练。","audio":"audio/0237_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.262},{"id":238,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"The user hits the pads, and the arms give feedback, so the user has to dodge, roll or move under them.","literal_zh":"用户点击垫子，手臂给出反馈，所以用户必须在垫子下躲避，滚动或移动.","audio":"audio/0238_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.87},{"id":239,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Are the pads farther out than the screen?","literal_zh":"垫子离屏幕还远吗？","audio":"audio/0239_perrin.mp3","duration":3.158},{"id":240,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Is the screen recessed so the user cannot accidentally hit it?","literal_zh":"屏幕是关闭的，所以用户不能不小心击中它吗？","audio":"audio/0240_perrin.mp3","duration":4.526},{"id":241,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Exactly.","literal_zh":"没错","audio":"audio/0241_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.502},{"id":242,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"The user hits the pads, and the screen guides them on where to hit.","literal_zh":"用户点击垫子，屏幕引导他们到哪里点击.","audio":"audio/0242_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.262},{"id":243,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Good.","literal_zh":"不错","audio":"audio/0243_perrin.mp3","duration":1.79},{"id":244,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"That is important.","literal_zh":"这很重要。","audio":"audio/0244_perrin.mp3","duration":2.39},{"id":245,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"So the idea is that JabX can mix boxing classes, aerobic-style classes and high-intensity workouts.","literal_zh":"因此，这个想法是JabX可以混合拳击课，有氧风格的课和高强度的锻炼课.","audio":"audio/0245_interviewer.mp3","duration":6.71},{"id":246,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"It can teach movements like the jab, cross, hook, uppercut and dodge.","literal_zh":"它可以教授动作如刺，交叉，钩，上切和躲避.","audio":"audio/0246_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.838},{"id":247,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Ideally, it feels a bit like a coach holding pads for you.","literal_zh":"理想的情况是，它感觉有点像 教练为你拿着垫子。","audio":"audio/0247_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.638},{"id":248,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"And after the workout, there is a relaxation feature.","literal_zh":"锻炼后有一个放松的功能。","audio":"audio/0248_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.566},{"id":249,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Think of it a bit like a massage cooldown.","literal_zh":"想想看 有点像按摩冷却。","audio":"audio/0249_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.822},{"id":250,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"That is interesting.","literal_zh":"这很有趣。","audio":"audio/0250_perrin.mp3","duration":2.462},{"id":251,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"For beginners, it should start by teaching what the movements look like.","literal_zh":"对于初学者来说，它应该从教导运动的样子开始。","audio":"audio/0251_perrin.mp3","duration":4.91},{"id":252,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Then, as the user gets better, it can build into more complex combinations.","literal_zh":"然后，随着用户的提高，它可以构建成更复杂的组合.","audio":"audio/0252_perrin.mp3","duration":5.822},{"id":253,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Does it teach footwork too?","literal_zh":"它也教脚活吗？","audio":"audio/0253_perrin.mp3","duration":2.726},{"id":254,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Yes.","literal_zh":"对","audio":"audio/0254_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.118},{"id":255,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"The screen can show a real-person tutorial, and the AI movement recognition can give form corrections during the class.","literal_zh":"屏幕可以显示真人辅导，AI运动识别可以在上课期间给出形式校正.","audio":"audio/0255_interviewer.mp3","duration":7.07},{"id":256,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"That is good.","literal_zh":"这是很好的。","audio":"audio/0256_perrin.mp3","duration":2.198},{"id":257,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Footwork matters.","literal_zh":"脚活很重要。","audio":"audio/0257_perrin.mp3","duration":2.486},{"id":258,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"Boxing is not just about the hands.","literal_zh":"拳击不仅仅是手。","audio":"audio/0258_perrin.mp3","duration":3.326},{"id":259,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"JabX 硬件演示与动作反馈","english":"It is also about where your feet are, how you move and how you coordinate the whole body.","literal_zh":"这也是关于你的脚在哪里 如何移动 如何协调整个身体。","audio":"audio/0259_perrin.mp3","duration":5.534},{"id":260,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"So, gut reaction: how does the product concept land for you?","literal_zh":"那么，肠道反应: 产品概念如何为您服务？","audio":"audio/0260_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.902},{"id":261,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"I think it sounds interesting.","literal_zh":"我觉得这听起来很有趣。","audio":"audio/0261_perrin.mp3","duration":2.894},{"id":262,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"The moving-arm feature is different, and I like that.","literal_zh":"移动臂的功能不同 我喜欢","audio":"audio/0262_perrin.mp3","duration":4.166},{"id":263,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Most people learn jabs and uppercuts, but they do not always learn evasion, blocking or how to get out of the way.","literal_zh":"大多数人学习刺拳和上切拳，但他们并不总是学会逃避，阻拦或如何摆脱障碍.","audio":"audio/0263_perrin.mp3","duration":7.358},{"id":264,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Unless you have a real coach, that can be hard to practice.","literal_zh":"除非你有真正的教练 否则很难练习","audio":"audio/0264_perrin.mp3","duration":4.622},{"id":265,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"So if the machine can teach those movements, that is valuable.","literal_zh":"所以，如果机器能教这些动作，那是有价值的。","audio":"audio/0265_perrin.mp3","duration":4.718},{"id":266,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Be honest with us.","literal_zh":"对我们说实话","audio":"audio/0266_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.838},{"id":267,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Would the moving arms feel exciting, or would they make you a little nervous?","literal_zh":"动动的手臂会感到兴奋 还是会让你有点紧张？","audio":"audio/0267_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.694},{"id":268,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"I think that should be more of an advanced feature.","literal_zh":"我认为这应该是一个更先进的特点。","audio":"audio/0268_perrin.mp3","duration":3.614},{"id":269,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Beginners should start with the basic movements first.","literal_zh":"初学者应先从基本运动开始.","audio":"audio/0269_perrin.mp3","duration":3.998},{"id":270,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Then, once they are comfortable, the moving arms can be added.","literal_zh":"然后，一旦它们舒适，就可以添加移动的手臂.","audio":"audio/0270_perrin.mp3","duration":4.79},{"id":271,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"As long as the arms are not too aggressive or unsafe, I would be fine with it.","literal_zh":"只要手臂没有太冲动或不安全，我就可以了。","audio":"audio/0271_perrin.mp3","duration":5.414},{"id":272,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"They are there to teach you how to move.","literal_zh":"他们在那里教你如何移动。","audio":"audio/0272_perrin.mp3","duration":3.062},{"id":273,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Of everything we just walked through, what stood out to you the most?","literal_zh":"我们所经历的一切中，你最突出的是什么？","audio":"audio/0273_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.758},{"id":274,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"I like the idea that the system tells me what to do.","literal_zh":"我喜欢系统告诉我该怎么做的想法。","audio":"audio/0274_perrin.mp3","duration":4.094},{"id":275,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"I do not have to think too much.","literal_zh":"我不必想太多。","audio":"audio/0275_perrin.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":276,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"I can just follow along.","literal_zh":"我可以跟着你","audio":"audio/0276_perrin.mp3","duration":2.774},{"id":277,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"The lights that show where to hit are important, especially for beginners.","literal_zh":"显示击打地点的灯光很重要，特别是对初学者来说.","audio":"audio/0277_perrin.mp3","duration":5.102},{"id":278,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"But I also think users should be able to turn them off as they improve.","literal_zh":"但我也认为用户应该能够随着改进而关闭.","audio":"audio/0278_perrin.mp3","duration":4.814},{"id":279,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Once someone knows what they are doing, constant light prompts might become annoying.","literal_zh":"一旦有人知道他们在做什么， 恒定的光提示可能会变得烦人。","audio":"audio/0279_perrin.mp3","duration":5.462},{"id":280,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"A beginner may need them.","literal_zh":"初学者可能需要他们","audio":"audio/0280_perrin.mp3","duration":2.654},{"id":281,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"An intermediate user may still like them.","literal_zh":"一个中间用户可能仍然喜欢它们.","audio":"audio/0281_perrin.mp3","duration":3.566},{"id":282,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"But an advanced user may want less guidance.","literal_zh":"但高级用户可能想要较少的指导.","audio":"audio/0282_perrin.mp3","duration":3.662},{"id":283,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"I also like the evasion feature with the moving arms.","literal_zh":"我也喜欢用移动的手臂逃避","audio":"audio/0283_perrin.mp3","duration":3.998},{"id":284,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"Without another person there, it is hard to train that.","literal_zh":"没有其他人在那里，很难训练它。","audio":"audio/0284_perrin.mp3","duration":4.238},{"id":285,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"重点功能反馈：灯光、躲闪与进阶","english":"If the equipment can create that stimulus, the user does not have to guess.","literal_zh":"如果设备可以创造这种刺激，用户就不必猜测.","audio":"audio/0285_perrin.mp3","duration":5.39},{"id":286,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"For the AI coach, what would feel better to you: a male coach, a female coach or both?","literal_zh":"对AI教练来说，你感觉会更好:男教练，女教练还是两者兼而有之？","audio":"audio/0286_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.534},{"id":287,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"You should offer both.","literal_zh":"你应该提供两者。","audio":"audio/0287_perrin.mp3","duration":2.558},{"id":288,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Some women may relate more to a female coach.","literal_zh":"一些妇女可能与女教练的关系更为密切。","audio":"audio/0288_perrin.mp3","duration":3.902},{"id":289,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Leila Ali could be a good example of a well-known female boxer.","literal_zh":"莱拉·阿里(英语:Leila Ali)可以是一个著名的女性拳击手的好例子.","audio":"audio/0289_perrin.mp3","duration":4.91},{"id":290,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"For male coaches, people know names like Mike Tyson or Muhammad Ali.","literal_zh":"对于男性教练来说，人们知道麦克·泰森或穆罕默德·阿里等名字.","audio":"audio/0290_perrin.mp3","duration":5.438},{"id":291,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Having both options is better because people connect with different types of coaches.","literal_zh":"拥有两种选择都更好，因为人们与不同类型的导师有联系.","audio":"audio/0291_perrin.mp3","duration":5.534},{"id":292,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"How much does the look of the machine matter to you?","literal_zh":"机器的外观对你有多重要？","audio":"audio/0292_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":293,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Color, style, the whole vibe.","literal_zh":"颜色 风格 整个气氛","audio":"audio/0293_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.366},{"id":294,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Some people like customization.","literal_zh":"有些人喜欢定制。","audio":"audio/0294_perrin.mp3","duration":3.182},{"id":295,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"They want a few color options.","literal_zh":"他们想要一些颜色选择。","audio":"audio/0295_perrin.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":296,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Black is always the safe choice.","literal_zh":"黑色总是安全的选择。","audio":"audio/0296_perrin.mp3","duration":3.254},{"id":297,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"It fits most home gyms.","literal_zh":"它适合大多数的家体育馆。","audio":"audio/0297_perrin.mp3","duration":2.87},{"id":298,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"White can look clean and modern, but it may not fit every gym as well as black.","literal_zh":"白色可以看起来干净和现代，但可能不适合每一个健身房和黑色.","audio":"audio/0298_perrin.mp3","duration":5.486},{"id":299,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Our home gym has blue and red accents, so blue or red options would be interesting to us.","literal_zh":"我们家的体育馆有蓝色和红色的口音，所以蓝色或红色的选择对我们来说是有趣的.","audio":"audio/0299_perrin.mp3","duration":6.542},{"id":300,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"Some people design their gym around a certain color.","literal_zh":"有些人用某种颜色设计自己的健身房.","audio":"audio/0300_perrin.mp3","duration":3.926},{"id":301,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"AI 教练形象与设备外观","english":"But if you can only choose one color, I would go with black.","literal_zh":"但是如果你只能选择一种颜色， 我会用黑色的。","audio":"audio/0301_perrin.mp3","duration":4.406},{"id":302,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"We are also playing with a game mode that works more like a rhythm game.","literal_zh":"我们还在玩一种更像节奏游戏的游戏模式。","audio":"audio/0302_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.974},{"id":303,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"You hit the pads along with the music.","literal_zh":"你和音乐一起打垫子","audio":"audio/0303_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.702},{"id":304,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"I like that.","literal_zh":"我喜欢","audio":"audio/0304_perrin.mp3","duration":2.294},{"id":305,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"It reminds me of dance games where you step on the squares to the music, or VR games where you punch targets in the air.","literal_zh":"它让我想起了舞蹈游戏，你踩在广场上的音乐，或者VR游戏，你在空中打靶.","audio":"audio/0305_perrin.mp3","duration":7.67},{"id":306,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"That kind of game helps with hand-eye coordination.","literal_zh":"这种游戏有助于手眼的协调。","audio":"audio/0306_perrin.mp3","duration":3.878},{"id":307,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"Your eyes see the target, and your hands react.","literal_zh":"你的眼睛看到目标，你的手反应。","audio":"audio/0307_perrin.mp3","duration":3.926},{"id":308,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"I also like gamification in general.","literal_zh":"我也喜欢游戏一般。","audio":"audio/0308_perrin.mp3","duration":3.518},{"id":309,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"It makes the workout more exciting.","literal_zh":"这让锻炼更刺激.","audio":"audio/0309_perrin.mp3","duration":3.158},{"id":310,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"I am competitive, so if you give me a score based on how hard I hit, how many targets I hit or how I compare with my husband or kids, that sounds fun.","literal_zh":"我是有竞争力的，所以如果你给我一个分数 依据我打的多重，我打的多少目标， 或者我如何比较我的丈夫或孩子， 这听起来很有趣。","audio":"audio/0310_perrin.mp3","duration":9.926},{"id":311,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"In another version, you would hit the pads to the beat while the moving arms come in, so you have to duck or dodge too.","literal_zh":"在另一种版本中，你会在移动的手臂进来时撞到拍子上的垫子，所以你还必须躲开或躲避.","audio":"audio/0311_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.87},{"id":312,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"That sounds fun.","literal_zh":"这听起来很有趣。","audio":"audio/0312_perrin.mp3","duration":2.438},{"id":313,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"I would be interested in that.","literal_zh":"我对此有兴趣。","audio":"audio/0313_perrin.mp3","duration":2.87},{"id":314,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"We are also thinking about multiplayer.","literal_zh":"我们还在考虑多人游戏。","audio":"audio/0314_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.822},{"id":315,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"Picture one person on the left, one on the right, both playing at the same time.","literal_zh":"想象左边一人，右边一人，都同时演奏.","audio":"audio/0315_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.598},{"id":316,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"That could be cool, as long as the setup is safe for two people.","literal_zh":"那可能很酷 只要对两个人安全","audio":"audio/0316_perrin.mp3","duration":4.79},{"id":317,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"What about a phone-control mode?","literal_zh":"电话控制模式呢？","audio":"audio/0317_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.342},{"id":318,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"Say your son is on the app while you are training, and he can change the pads or moving arms in real time.","literal_zh":"说你儿子在接受训练时正在应用 他可以实时更换垫子或移动手臂","audio":"audio/0318_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.99},{"id":319,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"My sons would love that.","literal_zh":"我儿子会喜欢的","audio":"audio/0319_perrin.mp3","duration":2.75},{"id":320,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"They would enjoy controlling it and making the workout harder for us.","literal_zh":"他们喜欢控制它，让我们更难解决。","audio":"audio/0320_perrin.mp3","duration":4.622},{"id":321,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"游戏模式、多人互动与手机控制","english":"That could be a fun family feature.","literal_zh":"这可能是一个有趣的家庭特色。","audio":"audio/0321_perrin.mp3","duration":3.23},{"id":322,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I noticed the Apple Watch.","literal_zh":"我注意到苹果观察。","audio":"audio/0322_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.126},{"id":323,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"Are you using that mainly for fitness tracking, or more for everyday stuff?","literal_zh":"你主要用来追踪身体状况 还是用来做日常工作？","audio":"audio/0323_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.718},{"id":324,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I wear both an Apple Watch and a WHOOP.","literal_zh":"我戴着苹果表和WOOP","audio":"audio/0324_perrin.mp3","duration":3.23},{"id":325,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I charge my Apple Watch at night, so most of my sleep and heart-rate data comes from WHOOP.","literal_zh":"晚上我收取苹果表，所以我大部分睡眠和心率数据来自WHOOP.","audio":"audio/0325_perrin.mp3","duration":6.014},{"id":326,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I mostly use the Apple Watch for steps, texts, emails and notifications.","literal_zh":"我主要使用苹果观察 的步骤，短信，电子邮件和通知。","audio":"audio/0326_perrin.mp3","duration":6.182},{"id":327,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"For health data, I rely more on WHOOP.","literal_zh":"关于健康数据，我更依赖WHOOP.","audio":"audio/0327_perrin.mp3","duration":3.494},{"id":328,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"With WHOOP, I track sleep, heart-rate zones, strain and recovery.","literal_zh":"用WHOOP，我跟踪睡眠，心率区，紧张和复苏。","audio":"audio/0328_perrin.mp3","duration":5.414},{"id":329,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I start an activity for every workout, whether it is lifting, walking, running, swimming, cardio or boxing.","literal_zh":"我开始每个运动， 无论是举起，步行，跑步，游泳，心跳还是拳击。","audio":"audio/0329_perrin.mp3","duration":8.246},{"id":330,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"WHOOP uses my heart rate to calculate strain, and that affects my recovery score.","literal_zh":"WHOOP用我的心率来计算压力， 这影响了我的恢复分数.","audio":"audio/0330_perrin.mp3","duration":5.99},{"id":331,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"Every morning, I check my sleep, strain and recovery.","literal_zh":"每天早上，我检查我的睡眠，紧张和康复。","audio":"audio/0331_perrin.mp3","duration":4.766},{"id":332,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"If my recovery is in the red, I know I should not push as hard that day.","literal_zh":"如果我的康复是红色的，我知道我不应该 推那么用力的那一天。","audio":"audio/0332_perrin.mp3","duration":5.078},{"id":333,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I mostly look for patterns.","literal_zh":"我主要寻找规律","audio":"audio/0333_perrin.mp3","duration":2.99},{"id":334,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I want to know what affects my recovery.","literal_zh":"我想知道什么影响我的康复。","audio":"audio/0334_perrin.mp3","duration":3.374},{"id":335,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"WHOOP often tells me to go to bed earlier or keep my sleep schedule more consistent.","literal_zh":"WHOOP经常让我早点上床，或者保持睡眠时间的一致.","audio":"audio/0335_perrin.mp3","duration":5.822},{"id":336,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"WHOOP is not great for steps yet, so I still use Apple Watch for that.","literal_zh":"WHOOP对台阶还不太好，所以我仍然使用苹果观察来做这个.","audio":"audio/0336_perrin.mp3","duration":5.222},{"id":337,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"Do you ever use the AI features in WHOOP?","literal_zh":"你有没有使用过WHOOP中的AI功能？","audio":"audio/0337_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.846},{"id":338,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"Sometimes, but not as much as I could.","literal_zh":"有时候，但没我能做多少。","audio":"audio/0338_perrin.mp3","duration":3.662},{"id":339,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I work for a marketing company, and we use AI a lot, so I can get a little overloaded with it.","literal_zh":"我为一家营销公司工作，我们经常使用AI，这样我就可以有点超载.","audio":"audio/0339_perrin.mp3","duration":6.59},{"id":340,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"One way I used WHOOP AI was to add a 10-minute warm-up walk before every lifting day.","literal_zh":"我使用WHOOP AI的方法之一是在每个升起日之前增加一个10分钟的热身步行.","audio":"audio/0340_perrin.mp3","duration":6.134},{"id":341,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"可穿戴设备与健康数据","english":"I told it what I wanted, and it added that warm-up to my WHOOP schedule.","literal_zh":"我告诉它我想要的， 它增加了热身 我的WHOP时间表。","audio":"audio/0341_perrin.mp3","duration":4.982},{"id":342,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"How big is Tonal in your world?","literal_zh":"托纳尔在你的世界里有多大？","audio":"audio/0342_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.486},{"id":343,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"Do people around you use it or talk about it much?","literal_zh":"你周围的人用它或谈论它很多？","audio":"audio/0343_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.254},{"id":344,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"Tonal has a large community, especially on Facebook.","literal_zh":"Tonal有一个庞大的社区，特别是在Facebook上.","audio":"audio/0344_perrin.mp3","duration":4.502},{"id":345,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"When we first started our channel, we wanted to show Tonal users how they could combine Tonal with other home gym equipment and accessories.","literal_zh":"当我们开始频道时，我们想向Tonal用户展示Tonal与其他家庭体育器材和配件如何结合.","audio":"audio/0345_perrin.mp3","duration":8.51},{"id":346,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"We wanted to show a more hybrid setup.","literal_zh":"我们想展示一个更混合的设定。","audio":"audio/0346_perrin.mp3","duration":3.254},{"id":347,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"It did not have to be only Tonal.","literal_zh":"不一定只用Tonal来做","audio":"audio/0347_perrin.mp3","duration":3.158},{"id":348,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"But Tonal is fairly restrictive about what you can share if it is not through them.","literal_zh":"但是，Tonal对于你能够分享的，如果不通过它们，是相当有限的。","audio":"audio/0348_perrin.mp3","duration":5.198},{"id":349,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"So we moved away from focusing on that.","literal_zh":"于是我们不再关注这个问题。","audio":"audio/0349_perrin.mp3","duration":3.494},{"id":350,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"The biggest complaint people have about Tonal is the monthly subscription.","literal_zh":"人们对Tonal最大的抱怨是每月订阅.","audio":"audio/0350_perrin.mp3","duration":5.078},{"id":351,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"If you cancel the membership, you lose many of the smart features.","literal_zh":"如果取消会员资格，就会失去许多智能功能.","audio":"audio/0351_perrin.mp3","duration":4.814},{"id":352,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"You can still use the machine, but it becomes more like an expensive functional trainer on the wall.","literal_zh":"仍然可以使用机器，但变得更像是墙上昂贵的功能教练.","audio":"audio/0352_perrin.mp3","duration":6.374},{"id":353,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"People say similar things about Peloton.","literal_zh":"人们对佩洛顿也有类似的说法.","audio":"audio/0353_perrin.mp3","duration":3.542},{"id":354,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"I understand why companies charge subscriptions.","literal_zh":"我知道为什么公司要收订阅费","audio":"audio/0354_perrin.mp3","duration":4.07},{"id":355,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"They need to maintain programs, coaches and classes.","literal_zh":"他们需要保持程序，教练和班级.","audio":"audio/0355_perrin.mp3","duration":4.334},{"id":356,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"But if you can create a great experience without forcing a monthly fee, that is a strong selling point.","literal_zh":"但是，如果你可以创造一个伟大的经验 而不强制每月收费， 这是一个强大的销售点。","audio":"audio/0356_perrin.mp3","duration":6.854},{"id":357,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"One option is to include a basic set of programs with the machine and then sell extra program bundles.","literal_zh":"一个选项是包含一套与机器一起的基本程序，然后出售额外的程序捆绑.","audio":"audio/0357_perrin.mp3","duration":6.926},{"id":358,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"For example, users could pay for a pack of 10 new workouts if they want more variety.","literal_zh":"例如，用户如果想要更多种类，可以支付一包10个新工作.","audio":"audio/0358_perrin.mp3","duration":6.062},{"id":359,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"That gives you revenue without making everyone pay a subscription.","literal_zh":"这样你就能赚到收入了 不必让每个人都付订金","audio":"audio/0359_perrin.mp3","duration":4.742},{"id":360,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"WHOOP is subscription-based too.","literal_zh":"WHOOP也以订阅为基础.","audio":"audio/0360_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.39},{"id":361,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"How do you feel about that model?","literal_zh":"你觉得那个模特怎么样？","audio":"audio/0361_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.294},{"id":362,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"That is one thing I do not love.","literal_zh":"这是我不爱的一件事。","audio":"audio/0362_perrin.mp3","duration":3.158},{"id":363,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"WHOOP does offer family plans and tiered plans, which helps.","literal_zh":"WHOOP确实提供家庭计划和分层计划，这有帮助。","audio":"audio/0363_perrin.mp3","duration":4.934},{"id":364,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"My husband has a higher tier than I do because he wanted some extra features.","literal_zh":"我丈夫有比我更高的层次 因为他想要一些额外的特征。","audio":"audio/0364_perrin.mp3","duration":5.486},{"id":365,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"I think tiers can work if people clearly understand what they are paying for.","literal_zh":"我认为，如果人们清楚地了解他们付出的代价，等级可以发挥作用。","audio":"audio/0365_perrin.mp3","duration":5.39},{"id":366,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"For JabX, you could have a basic package with the core features.","literal_zh":"对于JabX，你可以有一个具有核心特征的基本包.","audio":"audio/0366_perrin.mp3","duration":4.886},{"id":367,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"Tonal、订阅模式与内容付费","english":"Then you could offer higher tiers for people who want new programs, extra features or ongoing content.","literal_zh":"然后，你可以为需要新程序、额外功能或持续内容的人提供更高层次的服务。","audio":"audio/0367_perrin.mp3","duration":7.118},{"id":368,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Given everything we described, what price range would feel fair for JabX if there were no required subscription?","literal_zh":"鉴于我们所描述的一切，如果没有必要的订阅，JabX会觉得什么价格范围是公平的？","audio":"audio/0368_interviewer.mp3","duration":6.11},{"id":369,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"I do not know your manufacturing cost or margins, so it is hard to say exactly.","literal_zh":"我不知道你的制造成本和利润 所以很难说清楚","audio":"audio/0369_perrin.mp3","duration":6.062},{"id":370,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"But Tonal is around $4,200, and some of what you described feels similar in value.","literal_zh":"但Tonal大约是4200美元， 你描述的一些东西也觉得价值相似。","audio":"audio/0370_perrin.mp3","duration":7.286},{"id":371,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"If JabX includes the hardware, AI features, training programs and game functions you mentioned, around $4,000 sounds reasonable to me.","literal_zh":"如果JabX包含你提到的硬件，AI功能，培训程序和游戏功能，大约4000美元对我来说是合理的.","audio":"audio/0371_perrin.mp3","duration":9.902},{"id":372,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"For coaching, would you rather see AI-generated coaches, real human coaches or maybe both?","literal_zh":"关于教练，你宁愿看AI产生的教练，真正的人类教练，还是两者兼而有之？","audio":"audio/0372_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.27},{"id":373,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"One thing that really sells Tonal is the real coaches.","literal_zh":"真正卖Tonal的是真正的导师","audio":"audio/0373_perrin.mp3","duration":4.31},{"id":374,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Users can watch them, connect with them and feel like they know them.","literal_zh":"用户可以观看它们，与它们连接，并感觉他们了解它们.","audio":"audio/0374_perrin.mp3","duration":4.838},{"id":375,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Tonal also has Facebook groups where coaches interact with users, answer questions and lead challenges.","literal_zh":"Tonal也拥有脸书组，导师与用户互动，回答问题并领导挑战.","audio":"audio/0375_perrin.mp3","duration":7.358},{"id":376,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"That community connection is a big selling point.","literal_zh":"社区联系是一个大卖点。","audio":"audio/0376_perrin.mp3","duration":4.142},{"id":377,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"You do not need a huge number of coaches.","literal_zh":"你不需要很多教练","audio":"audio/0377_perrin.mp3","duration":3.566},{"id":378,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"You could start with one male coach and one female coach.","literal_zh":"你可以从一个男教练和一个女教练开始","audio":"audio/0378_perrin.mp3","duration":4.358},{"id":379,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"But having real people lead programs, run challenges and talk to the community can be powerful.","literal_zh":"但让真人领导节目，主持挑战，与社区交谈，可以很有力量.","audio":"audio/0379_perrin.mp3","duration":6.71},{"id":380,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Some users need that social connection to stay motivated.","literal_zh":"有些用户需要这种社会联系才能保持积极性。","audio":"audio/0380_perrin.mp3","duration":4.31},{"id":381,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Others, like my younger son, just want to get in, do the workout and leave.","literal_zh":"其他人，比如我小儿子， 只想进去，做锻炼和离开。","audio":"audio/0381_perrin.mp3","duration":5.702},{"id":382,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"You need to think about both types of users.","literal_zh":"你需要考虑两种类型的用户.","audio":"audio/0382_perrin.mp3","duration":3.59},{"id":383,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Do those coaches need to be famous, or is credibility the bigger thing?","literal_zh":"这些导师需要出名，还是信誉是更重要的事？","audio":"audio/0383_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.574},{"id":384,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Fame does not matter that much to me.","literal_zh":"名声对我不重要","audio":"audio/0384_perrin.mp3","duration":3.254},{"id":385,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Fame does not always mean someone is good.","literal_zh":"名声并不总是意味着某人是好人。","audio":"audio/0385_perrin.mp3","duration":3.494},{"id":386,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"Credibility matters more.","literal_zh":"可信度更为重要。","audio":"audio/0386_perrin.mp3","duration":2.846},{"id":387,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"If a very skinny person is trying to teach me how to build muscle, that is hard for me to believe.","literal_zh":"如果一个非常瘦的人试图教我如何建立肌肉，那对我来说很难相信.","audio":"audio/0387_perrin.mp3","duration":6.59},{"id":388,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"If someone who appears very out of shape is teaching cardio, some users may struggle to trust them.","literal_zh":"如果某个看起来非常不健全的人在教心术，一些用户可能难以相信他们.","audio":"audio/0388_perrin.mp3","duration":6.686},{"id":389,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"I know appearance is not always a true measure of health.","literal_zh":"我知道外表并不总是真正的健康标准","audio":"audio/0389_perrin.mp3","duration":4.118},{"id":390,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"But from a marketing point of view, image does matter.","literal_zh":"但从营销角度看，形象确实很重要.","audio":"audio/0390_perrin.mp3","duration":4.166},{"id":391,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"The coach does not have to be famous, but they should look credible for what they are teaching.","literal_zh":"教练虽然不必出名，但他们应该以自己所教的东西看起来可信.","audio":"audio/0391_perrin.mp3","duration":5.75},{"id":392,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"设备定价、真实教练与社区运营","english":"They should also come across as supportive and competent.","literal_zh":"他们也应该表现出支持性和胜任性。","audio":"audio/0392_perrin.mp3","duration":4.022},{"id":393,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"You seem really disciplined.","literal_zh":"你看起来很守纪律","audio":"audio/0393_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.126},{"id":394,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"What keeps you going?","literal_zh":"什么让你继续？","audio":"audio/0394_interviewer.mp3","duration":1.79},{"id":395,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"And what could JabX do for people who need a little more help staying consistent?","literal_zh":"JabX能为需要更多帮助的人做些什么？","audio":"audio/0395_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.55},{"id":396,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Gamification can help a lot.","literal_zh":"赌博可以帮助很多。","audio":"audio/0396_perrin.mp3","duration":3.134},{"id":397,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"WHOOP shows streaks and milestones, like how many days you have used it.","literal_zh":"WHOOP显示的历程和里程碑， 就像你用了多少天。","audio":"audio/0397_perrin.mp3","duration":5.03},{"id":398,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"For me, I do not want to break a streak.","literal_zh":"对我来说，我不想打破历史。","audio":"audio/0398_perrin.mp3","duration":3.614},{"id":399,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"If I am at 400 days, I do not want that number to go back to zero.","literal_zh":"如果我在400天，我不希望这个数字回到零。","audio":"audio/0399_perrin.mp3","duration":5.39},{"id":400,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I am a data person.","literal_zh":"我是一个数据人。","audio":"audio/0400_perrin.mp3","duration":2.582},{"id":401,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I love numbers.","literal_zh":"我喜欢数字","audio":"audio/0401_perrin.mp3","duration":2.414},{"id":402,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Discipline is not always something you can teach.","literal_zh":"纪律并不总是你能教的","audio":"audio/0402_perrin.mp3","duration":3.782},{"id":403,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"It has to come from inside the person.","literal_zh":"它必须来自人体内。","audio":"audio/0403_perrin.mp3","duration":3.278},{"id":404,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"But motivation can support discipline.","literal_zh":"但动机可以支持纪律。","audio":"audio/0404_perrin.mp3","duration":3.494},{"id":405,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Some people are motivated by streaks.","literal_zh":"有些人的动机是连锁店。","audio":"audio/0405_perrin.mp3","duration":3.518},{"id":406,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Some are motivated by fun.","literal_zh":"有些是出于乐趣","audio":"audio/0406_perrin.mp3","duration":2.942},{"id":407,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Some need a bigger goal.","literal_zh":"有些人需要更大的目标。","audio":"audio/0407_perrin.mp3","duration":2.606},{"id":408,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"For my husband and me, the goal is to live longer for our children and future grandchildren.","literal_zh":"对于我丈夫和我来说，目标是为我们的孩子和未来的孙子们长寿.","audio":"audio/0408_perrin.mp3","duration":6.182},{"id":409,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"That keeps us going, even on days when we do not feel like working out.","literal_zh":"这让我们继续前进，即使在我们不想工作的日子。","audio":"audio/0409_perrin.mp3","duration":5.078},{"id":410,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"If JabX is engaging, fun and personalized, people are more likely to keep using it.","literal_zh":"如果JabX正在参与，有趣和个性化，人们更有可能继续使用.","audio":"audio/0410_perrin.mp3","duration":6.422},{"id":411,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Coach interaction, programs, data, streaks, games and adaptive training could all help.","literal_zh":"教练互动、程序、数据、赛程、比赛和适应性训练都可能有所帮助。","audio":"audio/0411_perrin.mp3","duration":6.758},{"id":412,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Since you are a data person, do you track VO2 max?","literal_zh":"既然你是一个数据人， 你跟踪VO2最大？","audio":"audio/0412_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.566},{"id":413,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Yes.","literal_zh":"对","audio":"audio/0413_perrin.mp3","duration":1.958},{"id":414,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I have done DEXA scans, RMR tests and VO2 testing.","literal_zh":"我做了DEXA扫描，RMR测试和VO2测试.","audio":"audio/0414_perrin.mp3","duration":5.222},{"id":415,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"A DEXA scan gives information like body mass, body fat, body weight and bone density.","literal_zh":"DEXA扫描给出了身体质量，身体脂肪，体重和骨密度等信息.","audio":"audio/0415_perrin.mp3","duration":6.614},{"id":416,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"RMR testing looks at metabolism.","literal_zh":"RMR测试研究的是新陈代谢.","audio":"audio/0416_perrin.mp3","duration":3.47},{"id":417,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"VO2 testing measures cardio output.","literal_zh":"VO2测试测量心肌输出.","audio":"audio/0417_perrin.mp3","duration":3.782},{"id":418,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I also track HRV.","literal_zh":"我也追踪HRV","audio":"audio/0418_perrin.mp3","duration":2.894},{"id":419,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I like data, so the more useful data a machine can give me, the better.","literal_zh":"我喜欢数据，所以机器能给我的更有用的数据越好。","audio":"audio/0419_perrin.mp3","duration":5.342},{"id":420,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Would you ever plan workouts specifically to improve VO2 max?","literal_zh":"你是否打算过特别的 改进VO2最大吗？","audio":"audio/0420_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.358},{"id":421,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Not right now, because my main goal is building muscle.","literal_zh":"现在不行 因为我的主要目标是建立肌肉","audio":"audio/0421_perrin.mp3","duration":4.502},{"id":422,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"But I do want to improve my heart-rate zones and cardio output when I do cardio.","literal_zh":"但我确实想改善心率区 和心肌输出 当我做心肌。","audio":"audio/0422_perrin.mp3","duration":5.558},{"id":423,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"If I improve my cardio through boxing, it should also help my running pace and VO2 max.","literal_zh":"如果我通过拳击来改进我的心律，它也应该帮助我的跑步速度和VO2最大.","audio":"audio/0423_perrin.mp3","duration":6.662},{"id":424,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I may not train directly for VO2 max, but I would watch the connection.","literal_zh":"我可能不会直接训练 VO2最大， 但我会看连接。","audio":"audio/0424_perrin.mp3","duration":5.51},{"id":425,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"When you do cardio, are you watching your heart-rate zones in real time?","literal_zh":"当你做心跳的时候，你是否在实时观察你的心率区？","audio":"audio/0425_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.142},{"id":426,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"Yes.","literal_zh":"对","audio":"audio/0426_perrin.mp3","duration":1.958},{"id":427,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I usually keep my WHOOP app open so I can see my strain and heart-rate zone.","literal_zh":"我通常保持我的WOOP应用打开，这样我就能看到我的菌株和心率区.","audio":"audio/0427_perrin.mp3","duration":5.366},{"id":428,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"My WHOOP connects to my treadmill, so it can track my zone.","literal_zh":"我的WOOP连接到我的跑步机， 这样它就可以跟踪我的区域。","audio":"audio/0428_perrin.mp3","duration":4.622},{"id":429,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"I can set the treadmill to keep me in a target heart-rate zone.","literal_zh":"我可以设置跑步机 让我进入目标心率区","audio":"audio/0429_perrin.mp3","duration":4.526},{"id":430,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"自律、动机与数据驱动训练","english":"If my heart rate drops, the treadmill can automatically increase speed or incline to bring it back up.","literal_zh":"如果我的心率下降， 跑步机可以自动增加速度或线条 使其恢复。","audio":"audio/0430_perrin.mp3","duration":6.878},{"id":431,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"If JabX were in your home gym, would it replace something, or would it be more of an add-on?","literal_zh":"如果JabX在你家里的健身房， 它会替换什么， 还是更像是附加？","audio":"audio/0431_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.198},{"id":432,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"It would be an add-on.","literal_zh":"这将是一个附加。","audio":"audio/0432_perrin.mp3","duration":2.462},{"id":433,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"It would not replace anything.","literal_zh":"它不会取代任何东西。","audio":"audio/0433_perrin.mp3","duration":2.87},{"id":434,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"The treadmill is the one cardio machine we use regularly, and we will probably always keep it because it is so versatile.","literal_zh":"跑步机是我们经常使用的一种心肺机，我们可能永远保留它，因为它非常多功能。","audio":"audio/0434_perrin.mp3","duration":7.814},{"id":435,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"We got rid of the bike and rower because we did not use them enough, but the treadmill has always stayed useful.","literal_zh":"我们摆脱了自行车和划船机，因为我们没有充分利用它们，但跑步机一直有用.","audio":"audio/0435_perrin.mp3","duration":6.926},{"id":436,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"We are open to adding equipment if we think we will use it.","literal_zh":"我们愿意增加设备，如果我们想使用它。","audio":"audio/0436_perrin.mp3","duration":4.286},{"id":437,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"If something does not get used much, we usually sell it to someone who will use it more.","literal_zh":"如果用得不多的话，我们通常会把它卖给会多用它的人。","audio":"audio/0437_perrin.mp3","duration":5.846},{"id":438,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"What do you think about a built-in glove dryer?","literal_zh":"内置手套烘干机怎么样？","audio":"audio/0438_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.774},{"id":439,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"It would be an add-on, probably around $50.","literal_zh":"这将是一个附加， 大概50美元左右。","audio":"audio/0439_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.398},{"id":440,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"I think some people would like that.","literal_zh":"我想有些人会喜欢的","audio":"audio/0440_perrin.mp3","duration":3.086},{"id":441,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"For me, the big thing is storage.","literal_zh":"对我来说，大事情是储存。","audio":"audio/0441_perrin.mp3","duration":3.47},{"id":442,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"I do not want to store gloves somewhere else.","literal_zh":"我不想在别处存放手套","audio":"audio/0442_perrin.mp3","duration":3.47},{"id":443,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"I want them on the unit so I can grab them when I am ready to train.","literal_zh":"我要他们加入部队 等我准备好训练时再抓他们","audio":"audio/0443_perrin.mp3","duration":4.694},{"id":444,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"If the unit has glove storage and drying, that is useful.","literal_zh":"如果这个单位有手套储存和干燥，那是有用的.","audio":"audio/0444_perrin.mp3","duration":4.478},{"id":445,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"It also helps with smell because the gloves can dry properly.","literal_zh":"这也有助于嗅觉，因为手套可以适当干燥.","audio":"audio/0445_perrin.mp3","duration":4.55},{"id":446,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"I would pay $50 for that because it is not just drying.","literal_zh":"我愿意为此付出50美元，因为它不仅仅是干燥。","audio":"audio/0446_perrin.mp3","duration":4.598},{"id":447,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"It is also storage.","literal_zh":"它也是储存的。","audio":"audio/0447_perrin.mp3","duration":2.63},{"id":448,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"What about resistance bands as an add-on?","literal_zh":"抵抗乐队作为附加？","audio":"audio/0448_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.99},{"id":449,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"A lot of home gym users already have resistance bands.","literal_zh":"许多家用健身房用户已经拥有了抵抗乐队.","audio":"audio/0449_perrin.mp3","duration":4.502},{"id":450,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"We have a lot of them, so I probably would not buy them as an add-on.","literal_zh":"我们有很多，所以我可能不会买 作为附加。","audio":"audio/0450_perrin.mp3","duration":4.694},{"id":451,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"But for people who do not already have them, it could be useful.","literal_zh":"但是，对于还没有拥有它们的人来说，这可能是有益的。","audio":"audio/0451_perrin.mp3","duration":4.574},{"id":452,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"家庭健身房定位与配件反馈","english":"The price just needs to make sense because you can buy resistance bands on Amazon for around $35.","literal_zh":"价格需要合理 因为你可以在亚马逊购买约35美元的抵抗乐队.","audio":"audio/0452_perrin.mp3","duration":7.262},{"id":453,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"What do you think about body-composition tracking?","literal_zh":"你觉得身体结构跟踪怎么样？","audio":"audio/0453_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.23},{"id":454,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"For example, every time someone turns on JabX, it could scan their body and show how things change over time.","literal_zh":"例如，每当有人打开JabX时，它可以扫描他们的身体，显示事情如何随时间变化.","audio":"audio/0454_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.99},{"id":455,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"I would be careful with accuracy.","literal_zh":"我会小心准确。","audio":"audio/0455_perrin.mp3","duration":3.11},{"id":456,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"There are a lot of scales and devices that claim to measure body composition, but they are not always fully accurate.","literal_zh":"有许多天平和装置声称要测量身体组成，但它们并不总是完全准确的.","audio":"audio/0456_perrin.mp3","duration":7.454},{"id":457,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"I would use that kind of data as a trend, not as an exact number.","literal_zh":"我将使用这种数据作为趋势，而不是确切的数字。","audio":"audio/0457_perrin.mp3","duration":4.934},{"id":458,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"If I scan myself one day and then see the number change consistently over time, that trend can be useful.","literal_zh":"如果有一天我扫描自己，然后看到数字随时间变化而变化，那么这种趋势就可能有用。","audio":"audio/0458_perrin.mp3","duration":7.334},{"id":459,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"But I would not fully trust the exact number.","literal_zh":"但我不会完全相信确切的数字。","audio":"audio/0459_perrin.mp3","duration":3.662},{"id":460,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"One type of body-composition scale uses sensors that you hold, and it sends a small current through the body.","literal_zh":"一种类型的身体结构尺度使用你持有的传感器，它通过身体发出小电流.","audio":"audio/0460_perrin.mp3","duration":7.07},{"id":461,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"That feels more credible to me than just using an image-based scan.","literal_zh":"我觉得比用图像扫描更可信","audio":"audio/0461_perrin.mp3","duration":4.862},{"id":462,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"身体数据扫描与趋势追踪","english":"I reviewed the Arboleaf scale on our YouTube channel, and in that review I talk about exact numbers versus trends.","literal_zh":"我在YouTube频道上回顾了Arboleaf比例表，","audio":"audio/0462_perrin.mp3","duration":7.622},{"id":463,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"You have seen the concept now.","literal_zh":"你现在看到了这个概念。","audio":"audio/0463_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.246},{"id":464,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Any questions for us, or anything you think we should be paying attention to?","literal_zh":"对我们有什么问题吗？ 或者你认为我们应该注意什么？","audio":"audio/0464_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.334},{"id":465,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"My main question is where you are in the launch process.","literal_zh":"我的主要疑问是你们在发射过程中的位置。","audio":"audio/0465_perrin.mp3","duration":4.142},{"id":466,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Do you have a target launch date?","literal_zh":"你有目标发射日期吗？","audio":"audio/0466_perrin.mp3","duration":2.87},{"id":467,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"We are aiming for August.","literal_zh":"我们的目标是8月。","audio":"audio/0467_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.246},{"id":468,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"We are also planning to be at CES in January in Las Vegas.","literal_zh":"我们还计划1月份在拉斯维加斯的CES。","audio":"audio/0468_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.238},{"id":469,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"August is soon.","literal_zh":"八月即时.","audio":"audio/0469_perrin.mp3","duration":2.39},{"id":470,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"CES is a major event.","literal_zh":"CES是一个重大事件。","audio":"audio/0470_perrin.mp3","duration":3.014},{"id":471,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Another event you may want to look at in the future is Home Gym Con.","literal_zh":"你将来可能想看的另外一个事件是Home Gym Con.","audio":"audio/0471_perrin.mp3","duration":4.766},{"id":472,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"It happens around the end of July or beginning of August.","literal_zh":"发生在7月底或8月初左右.","audio":"audio/0472_perrin.mp3","duration":4.406},{"id":473,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Jeff and I go every year.","literal_zh":"Jeff和我每年都去","audio":"audio/0473_perrin.mp3","duration":2.774},{"id":474,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"It has become a pretty large event, and it would be relevant for a product like this.","literal_zh":"它已经成为一个相当大的事件， 它将会与这样的产品有关。","audio":"audio/0474_perrin.mp3","duration":5.606},{"id":475,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"It may be too soon for this year, but it could be worth considering later.","literal_zh":"今年可能为时太早，但值得稍后考虑。","audio":"audio/0475_perrin.mp3","duration":5.174},{"id":476,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"We are not currently scheduled for CES, but my husband has wanted to go to Las Vegas, so we can look into it.","literal_zh":"我们目前没有安排CES， 但我的丈夫已经想去拉斯维加斯， 所以我们可以调查它。","audio":"audio/0476_perrin.mp3","duration":7.742},{"id":477,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"The channel is a second job for both of us, and we both work full-time, so we have to plan events around our main work schedules.","literal_zh":"该频道是我们俩的第二份工作，我们都是全职工作，所以我们必须围绕我们的主要工作时间表规划活动.","audio":"audio/0477_perrin.mp3","duration":8.27},{"id":478,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Would it be okay if we added you to our WhatsApp group and sent occasional updates?","literal_zh":"我们把你加入我们的WhatsApp小组 偶尔发送最新消息可以吗？","audio":"audio/0478_interviewer.mp3","duration":4.79},{"id":479,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Nothing crazy, maybe once a month.","literal_zh":"没什么疯狂的，也许一个月一次。","audio":"audio/0479_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.63},{"id":480,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Yes, that would be fine.","literal_zh":"是的，这将是罚款。","audio":"audio/0480_perrin.mp3","duration":2.99},{"id":481,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"We would love to stay updated.","literal_zh":"我们很乐意随时更新","audio":"audio/0481_perrin.mp3","duration":2.87},{"id":482,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"When the units are ready, if you want to send us one for review, we would be happy to test it.","literal_zh":"等部队准备好了 如果你想派一个来审查 我们很乐意测试一下","audio":"audio/0482_perrin.mp3","duration":6.206},{"id":483,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"When we review equipment, we do not just test it and publish criticism.","literal_zh":"当我们审查设备时，我们不仅测试设备并发表批评意见。","audio":"audio/0483_perrin.mp3","duration":5.246},{"id":484,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"While we are using it, we reach out to the vendor with questions and feedback.","literal_zh":"在我们使用时，我们向供应商提出问题和反馈。","audio":"audio/0484_perrin.mp3","duration":5.15},{"id":485,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"We may ask whether something is working as intended or whether a feature is supposed to work differently.","literal_zh":"我们可以问一问，某种东西是否如预期的那样起作用，或者某种特征是否应该不同地起作用。","audio":"audio/0485_perrin.mp3","duration":6.374},{"id":486,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"That gives the company a chance to explain, fix an issue or tell us if a future version is coming.","literal_zh":"这让公司有机会解释，解决一个问题，或者告诉我们未来的版本是否即将来临.","audio":"audio/0486_perrin.mp3","duration":6.734},{"id":487,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"For us, a review is a collaboration.","literal_zh":"对我们来说，审查是一种合作。","audio":"audio/0487_perrin.mp3","duration":3.734},{"id":488,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"We want to clearly communicate the value of the product and how the company is improving it.","literal_zh":"我们要明确宣传产品的价值和公司如何改进.","audio":"audio/0488_perrin.mp3","duration":5.774},{"id":489,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"One more fun question.","literal_zh":"还有一个有趣的问题。","audio":"audio/0489_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.006},{"id":490,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"If we invited you to Hong Kong to try the equipment in person, would that be something you might consider?","literal_zh":"如果我们邀请你到香港亲自去试设备 你会考虑一下吗？","audio":"audio/0490_interviewer.mp3","duration":5.726},{"id":491,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"I would need to talk to my husband about that, but I can get back to you.","literal_zh":"我需要和我的丈夫谈谈， 但我可以回到你。","audio":"audio/0491_perrin.mp3","duration":5.006},{"id":492,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"It is something we could consider.","literal_zh":"这是我们可以考虑的事情。","audio":"audio/0492_perrin.mp3","duration":2.894},{"id":493,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Thank you for all of this.","literal_zh":"谢谢你的帮助","audio":"audio/0493_interviewer.mp3","duration":2.03},{"id":494,"speaker":"Interviewer","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Seriously, your feedback has been really helpful.","literal_zh":"说真的 你的反馈很有帮助","audio":"audio/0494_interviewer.mp3","duration":3.278},{"id":495,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"I am excited about what you are creating.","literal_zh":"我为你创造的东西感到兴奋","audio":"audio/0495_perrin.mp3","duration":3.494},{"id":496,"speaker":"Perrin","section":"发布计划、展会与后续合作","english":"Feel free to reach out, and I will watch for the WhatsApp invite.","literal_zh":"随便你联系，我会看着WhatsApp的邀请。","audio":"audio/0496_perrin.mp3","duration":4.718}],"xingchen":[{"id":1,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Showroom Visit and Close-Range Teleoperation","section_zh":"一、展厅参观与近程遥操","english":"All right, let's start from the left side so the whole flow is easy to follow. The left side is our R&D area, so please don't take photos there; the right side is the showroom, and you are welcome to take pictures on that side. Next, I'll walk you through the teleoperation setup and show you a bit of what the model can do. For the model demo, I may need to check with my teammate on the exact startup steps, but this part right here is close-range teleoperation, and after I show it once, everyone can try it out.","literal_zh":"我们先从左边开始看。左边是研发区域，不允许拍照；右边是展厅区域，可以拍照。接下来我给大家展示一下技术遥操和模型能力。不过模型这一块如果要启动，我还需要问一下同事具体怎么操作。现在展示的是近程遥操，你们都可以上手试一下。","audio":null},{"id":2,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Showroom Visit and Close-Range Teleoperation","section_zh":"一、展厅参观与近程遥操","english":"You don't have to fully wear the device right now; just hang it around your neck for this part. Stand right here for a second, stay still, and now you're good to start operating.","literal_zh":"你不用把设备戴上，挂在脖子上就行。先站在这个位置，不要动，现在可以开始操作。","audio":null},{"id":3,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Showroom Visit and Close-Range Teleoperation","section_zh":"一、展厅参观与近程遥操","english":"The B button is for calibration, so that is always our first step. Did you feel the device vibrate? If not, calibration has not landed yet, so we need to do it again. Once it is calibrated, press A and the robot hand will come online, and when you need to stop, just press the stop button. If you bend forward, the robot bends forward with you, and it is much easier to feel that connection in person. Side-to-side bending is not supported in this position yet, because this joint can sway but cannot tilt like a human body. Later, with a spherical joint, we can open up more directions of motion.","literal_zh":"B 键是标定键，第一步就是标定。设备震动了吗？如果没有震动，就说明还没有标定成功。标定后按 A 键，手部就会启动。这个时候再按终止键。你往前弯腰，机器人就会跟着弯腰；但是左右方向现在还不行，因为这个位置只能晃动，不能像人一样倾斜。后续如果使用球形关节，就可以实现更多方向的动作。","audio":null},{"id":4,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Showroom Visit and Close-Range Teleoperation","section_zh":"一、展厅参观与近程遥操","english":"From a degrees-of-freedom point of view, it can get pretty close to the effect we want. The body is not really bending by itself; the motion is happening more at the end, and the nice part is that it also supports proportional control.","literal_zh":"从自由度上看，它可以达到类似效果。只是身体本身没有弯，实际弯曲的是末端。它还支持比例控制。","audio":null},{"id":5,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Showroom Visit and Close-Range Teleoperation","section_zh":"一、展厅参观与近程遥操","english":"This part is surprisingly precise, so go ahead and try inserting it here. The overall data-collection experience feels smooth, and once you try it, it is easier to understand than just watching me explain it.","literal_zh":"这个很精密。你可以把它插下去试试。整体数采体验还是比较流畅的。","audio":null},{"id":6,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Showroom Visit and Close-Range Teleoperation","section_zh":"一、展厅参观与近程遥操","english":"Everyone on our team has to pass this operation test, because once you know the posture, the workflow is very learnable. When you tap, hold it like this so the force can push back cleanly. If your hand gets loose, the device starts tilting up and down, so this posture keeps everything much steadier.","literal_zh":"这一套操作我们内部所有人都要考核，因为确实不算复杂。敲击时必须用这种姿势，力才能顶回来；如果松开，就会上下倾斜，所以这样操作会更稳。","audio":null},{"id":7,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Remote Teleoperation and Model Demo","section_zh":"二、远程遥操与模型 Demo","english":"To be honest, I still have not passed the remote teleoperation test myself, because I am not quite smooth enough with it yet. But the exciting part is that remote operation over the public internet does work. We tested Beijing to Shenzhen with latency roughly under 200 milliseconds, and later we also tested a Singapore link, which is basically ultra-long-distance teleoperation.","literal_zh":"实话说，我这个远程遥操考核一直没有通过，因为我自己还没有特别熟练。远程走公网这种方式可以做。我们测试过北京到深圳的公网链路，时延大概在两百毫秒以内；后来也测试过新加坡链路，算是超远程遥操。","audio":null},{"id":8,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Remote Teleoperation and Model Demo","section_zh":"二、远程遥操与模型 Demo","english":"The big thing with remote operation is not just getting the network to connect; it is keeping communication stable and latency under control. A public internet link can run, but that does not automatically make it production-ready. From what I understand, the current setup is more like waking the robot up remotely and letting it do slower actions. To make it truly production-grade, we still need stronger communication, steadier control, closed-loop task handling, and safety protection that you can really trust.","literal_zh":"不过，远程传输的核心问题其实还是通信稳定性和时延控制。公网链路能跑通，不代表它马上就能用于生产。我虽然没有看到完整的生产级实现，但我的理解是，它现在可能更多是把机器人启动起来，再慢慢执行一些动作。要真正达到生产级别，还需要解决通信、控制稳定性、任务闭环和安全保护等问题。","audio":null},{"id":9,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Remote Teleoperation and Model Demo","section_zh":"二、远程遥操与模型 Demo","english":"When you finish the whole operation, just press B, and then you can set the controller down.","literal_zh":"所有操作完成后，按 B 键就可以把手柄放下。","audio":null},{"id":10,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Remote Teleoperation and Model Demo","section_zh":"二、远程遥操与模型 Demo","english":"This robot is pretty tough, so don't be too nervous when you feel the feedback. Turn your wrist a little; yes, exactly like that. Now the reaction force can hold against you. Try pressing all the way down and you will feel the force feedback. Push a little harder and it will vibrate too, although the vibration comes in a bit slower. That reaction force travels through the joints and motors, and the robot body also has its own protective cover.","literal_zh":"我们机器人整体还是比较耐用的。把手腕转一下，对，这样反作用力就能顶住。你可以试着敲到底，它会有力反馈；再用力一点会震动，只是震动反馈会稍微慢一点。反作用力是通过关节和电机传递的，同时机器人本体也有防护罩。","audio":null},{"id":11,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Remote Teleoperation and Model Demo","section_zh":"二、远程遥操与模型 Demo","english":"It is actually hard to make the two hands fully touch. When they get close, you can feel this slight pull, almost like they want to snap together a little.","literal_zh":"两个手很难完全贴合在一起，靠近时会有一点吸附感。","audio":null},{"id":12,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Remote Teleoperation and Model Demo","section_zh":"二、远程遥操与模型 Demo","english":"One demo we have always wanted to build is a juggling demo, like throwing three balls at the same time. It would be such a fun model demo, but right now even manual teleoperation cannot do it cleanly yet, so doing it fully with a model is a much bigger challenge. Still, the long-term idea is exciting: if a human can do a motion, the robot has a real chance of learning it in the future.","literal_zh":"我们一直想做一个耍杂技的 demo，比如同时抛三个球。我们也想用模型做这种 demo，但现在人工遥操都还做不到，更不用说完全依靠模型。理论上，只要人能做到的动作，机器人未来大概率也能做到。","audio":null},{"id":13,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Tendon-Driven Structure and Mechanical Design","section_zh":"三、绳驱结构与机械设计","english":"Now let's switch gears and talk about production and the mechanical structure. You asked whether we have our own factories, and yes, we do: one in Wuxi and one in Bao'an.","literal_zh":"我们再说一下工厂生产和结构方案。你们问是不是自建工厂，我们在无锡有一个工厂，在宝安也有一个工厂。","audio":null},{"id":14,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Tendon-Driven Structure and Mechanical Design","section_zh":"三、绳驱结构与机械设计","english":"This structure uses tendon cables to drive the joints, so the force changes depending on the angle. For example, when the arm is held straight out, the S1 can stay level and keep working steadily. For the T1, the harder part is keeping the arm stable after it bends, and that is where the mechanical design really matters.","literal_zh":"我们这套结构是通过腱绳牵引来完成关节运动的。不同角度下，受力状态不一样。比如手臂平举时，S1 可以保持水平并稳定作业；T1 的难点在于，手臂弯曲之后还要保持稳定工作。","audio":null},{"id":15,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Tendon-Driven Structure and Mechanical Design","section_zh":"三、绳驱结构与机械设计","english":"The big win for a tendon-driven robot is that it is better for long working hours. Motor heat is a huge deal in robot design, because if the motor sits right at the joint, it keeps working whenever the arm moves, and that heat is hard to get rid of. Some designs use air cooling or liquid cooling, but that can hurt dust protection, water protection, and explosion-proof design. In real production environments, heat dissipation and protection are both a big deal.","literal_zh":"我觉得绳驱机器人的最大优势，是可以支持长时间作业。电机发热是机器人设计里的一个大问题。如果电机直接放在关节处，只要手臂运动，电机就要持续运转并发热，热量很难释放。现在很多方案会用风冷或液冷，但这样会影响整机的防尘、防水、防爆能力。对于生产环境来说，散热和防护都很关键。","audio":null},{"id":16,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Tendon-Driven Structure and Mechanical Design","section_zh":"三、绳驱结构与机械设计","english":"With a tendon-driven structure, we can keep the motors inside the body instead of putting them at the wrist or right at the joint end. That makes the end lighter, and it is friendlier for long-hour work. The tradeoff is that tendons can age, loosen, and become annoying to replace after long-term use. Also, tendon drive means you have to deal with multiple degrees of freedom, decoupling, forward kinematics, and inverse kinematics, so the control algorithm and the mechanical design both get more complicated.","literal_zh":"绳驱结构可以把电机放在身体内部，而不是放在手腕或关节末端。这样末端重量更轻，也更适合长时间工作。不过绳驱也有挑战，腱绳长期使用后会老化、松动，更换和维护也比较麻烦。另外，腱绳驱动涉及多个自由度之间的解耦和正逆解计算，控制算法和结构设计都会更复杂。","audio":null},{"id":17,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Tendon-Driven Structure and Mechanical Design","section_zh":"三、绳驱结构与机械设计","english":"Direct drive can definitely handle many tasks, and from a build perspective, it is simpler. You can work with a few factories and assemble a robot that way. But once the space is limited, balancing performance, weight, heat, and cost all at the same time gets tricky. The robot's real performance is not just about tendon drive versus direct drive. It also depends on kinematics, collision detection, interface adaptation, control delay, and how mature the whole system is.","literal_zh":"直驱方案不是不能完成任务。直驱确实更简单，找几个厂子组装一下也能做出一台机器。但要在有限空间里同时兼顾性能、重量、散热和成本，并不容易。真正影响机器人表现的，不只是绳驱还是直驱，还包括正逆解算法、碰撞检测、接口适配、控制延迟和系统整体成熟度。","audio":null},{"id":18,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Protection Modes, Load Capacity, and Safety Limits","section_zh":"四、保护模式、负载能力与安全边界","english":"This robot has built-in protection, kind of like limit protection. Once that protection is turned on, if there is a collision, the robot automatically goes into a protected state. Because this unit is here for showroom demos, we are running it in standard mode right now.","literal_zh":"这台机器人做了保护，类似限位保护。开启保护后，如果发生碰撞，机器人会自动进入保护状态。因为我是做展示用的，所以这台机器人目前使用标准模式。","audio":null},{"id":19,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Protection Modes, Load Capacity, and Safety Limits","section_zh":"四、保护模式、负载能力与安全边界","english":"Besides standard mode, there is an enhanced mode that can boost load, speed, and strength in a big way. Our R&D team told me it can reach around three times the standard mode, but I usually say at least double to keep the estimate conservative. Once the right parameters are set, the motor can run at full power.","literal_zh":"除了标准模式，还有一种增强模式，可以大幅提升负载、速度和力量。研发跟我说，最高可以提升到标准模式的三倍左右；我保守一点说，至少能提升两倍。给到相应参数后，电机就可以满功率运行。","audio":null},{"id":20,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Protection Modes, Load Capacity, and Safety Limits","section_zh":"四、保护模式、负载能力与安全边界","english":"For secondary development, you may not need those accounts at all. You can build on the standard robot-body parameters we provide, and if you stay within those standard parameters, you are totally fine. If a customer wants to push the robot closer to its limit, we can support that too, but the warranty needs a separate conversation. The reason is simple: the motors and related parts will be running much closer to full load, with much higher speed and force.","literal_zh":"如果是二次开发，实际上可能用不到这些账号。所有操作都可以基于我们提供的机器人本体参数标准来做，按照标准参数开发是完全没问题的。如果客户想追求极限性能，我们也可以支持，但质保需要另行约定，因为电机等部件会更接近满负荷运行，速度和力量都会明显提高。","audio":null},{"id":21,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Protection Modes, Load Capacity, and Safety Limits","section_zh":"四、保护模式、负载能力与安全边界","english":"The robot itself is strong, so when I operate it, using both hands together usually feels more natural. Our internal tests also have time targets; for example, the desktop cleaning task has to be finished within nineteen seconds. The showroom robots are mainly for customer demos, and the S1 is basically our flagship. When it reaches a limit position, motions like wrist rotation and arm extension are restricted by protection, and those protections really do work.","literal_zh":"机器人本身力气也很大。我之前用两只手配合操作，会更合适一些。内部考核也有时间要求，比如桌面清扫要在十九秒内完成。展厅里的机器人主要用于客户演示。S1 算是我们的旗舰机型。到达极限位置时，手腕、胳膊伸展等动作都会受到保护限制，这些保护是有效的。","audio":null},{"id":22,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Protection Modes, Load Capacity, and Safety Limits","section_zh":"四、保护模式、负载能力与安全边界","english":"My control setup is pretty easy to understand. The left joystick controls forward, backward, left, and right movement, and the right joystick controls the angle. There is also a mode where the robot follows a person, and so far, I have not run into any major issues with it.","literal_zh":"我的操作方式是：左边摇杆控制前后左右，右边摇杆控制角度。还有一个国内就是让机器人跟人一起走。目前我还没有遇到特别大的问题。","audio":null},{"id":23,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Protection Modes, Load Capacity, and Safety Limits","section_zh":"四、保护模式、负载能力与安全边界","english":"We can also use an electronic scale right here to show the load capacity, which makes the number feel much more real. When we say the T1 can carry about five kilograms, we mean it can still work steadily with the arm fully extended. Of course, the actual performance still depends on posture, speed, the end effector, and the task you are asking it to do.","literal_zh":"现场也可以通过电子秤做负载演示。我们说 T1 最大负载约五公斤，是指在手臂伸直的情况下依然能稳定作业。当然，具体表现还会受姿态、速度、末端执行器和任务类型影响。","audio":null},{"id":24,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Factory Production, Data Collection, and Aging Tests","section_zh":"五、工厂生产、数采与老化测试","english":"For production, R&D, data collection, and aging tests, we use dedicated robots. It is not like the structure team grabs one robot today and the electronics team borrows the exact same one tomorrow. Each type of work has its own relatively fixed machines, so the usage is much cleaner and easier to track.","literal_zh":"我们在生产、研发、数采、老化测试等环节都有固定设备。不会说结构工程师用一台，做板子的同事又把同一台借走。每类任务都有相对固定的机器人。","audio":null},{"id":25,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Factory Production, Data Collection, and Aging Tests","section_zh":"五、工厂生产、数采与老化测试","english":"The data-collection robots work hard, like seriously hard. Our data-collection team runs in three shifts, so one robot can be used continuously by three different operators. Based on the data from this April, some individual robots had already logged around 5,500 working hours, and by now that number should be even higher. Some units have already passed 6,000 hours.","literal_zh":"数采设备的使用强度比较高。我们有数采团队采用三班倒模式，一台机器人对应三名操作人员，持续用于数据采集。按今年四月份的数据，部分单台机器人累计工作时长大概是五千五百小时，现在应该更多。也有单机累计运行超过六千小时的情况。","audio":null},{"id":26,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Factory Production, Data Collection, and Aging Tests","section_zh":"五、工厂生产、数采与老化测试","english":"For aging tests, we have looked at what happens to the tendons after long-term use. The tendons do loosen over time, but we have units that only started losing accuracy after three years and three months of continuous use, and even then, the overall structure was still usable. Some units did not show obvious quality issues until around six years. So yes, tendons are long-term wear parts, but they can be reinforced or replaced during maintenance.","literal_zh":"老化测试方面，我们确实测过腱绳长期使用后的情况。腱绳在长期使用后会出现一定松动。我们有设备连续使用三年三个月后，精度才开始下降，但整体结构仍然可用。也有设备到六年后才出现明显质量问题。腱绳属于长期使用后会受影响的部件，后续可以通过加固或更换维护。","audio":null},{"id":27,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Factory Production, Data Collection, and Aging Tests","section_zh":"五、工厂生产、数采与老化测试","english":"I also asked what kinds of issues have appeared during delivery. For factory yield, if you build ten robots, a hundred robots, or a thousand robots, it is not realistic to expect every single unit to be perfect. Some small bugs or minor issues may leave the factory, and if they are not caught during post-production checks, they show up after delivery. Most other delivery issues are smaller after-sales items, usually around algorithm adaptation or port matching. So far, we have not had large-scale motor replacement or large-scale tendon replacement.","literal_zh":"我也问过交付过程中出现过哪些问题。比如工厂良品率方面，生产十台、一百台、一千台机器人，不可能每一台都完全没有问题。出厂时可能会有一些 bug 或小问题，如果生产后没有检测出来，就会在交付后暴露。其他交付问题多半是算法、端口适配等售后小问题。到目前为止，电机没有大规模更换过，腱绳也没有大规模更换过。","audio":null},{"id":28,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Factory Production, Data Collection, and Aging Tests","section_zh":"五、工厂生产、数采与老化测试","english":"The key parts can all be taken apart. This unit may be an early prototype used for debugging and positioning, so those markings are not random. During production, we add marks like this in many places to prevent assembly mistakes. Why would screws need to be replaced? Because vibration can make them shift. If the tendon or wiring is not aligned during inspection, that can turn into a problem later.","literal_zh":"关键部件都可以拆。这个可能是早期生产的样机，用来调试和定位。生产时为了做防呆定位，很多位置都会有类似标记。螺丝为什么要换？因为在震动过程中可能会偏移。如果检查时发现腱绳或线路对不准，就可能出现问题。","audio":null},{"id":29,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Product Versions, Pricing, and Delivery Schedule","section_zh":"六、产品版本、价格与交付排期","english":"Right now, the two main series worth focusing on are the S1 and the T1.","literal_zh":"现在主要聊 S1 和 T1 两个系列。","audio":null},{"id":30,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Product Versions, Pricing, and Delivery Schedule","section_zh":"六、产品版本、价格与交付排期","english":"The S1 is our flagship series, so it has stronger performance and a higher-end configuration, but of course the cost is higher too. We had a small amount of retail inventory before, and if you had come a few days earlier, you might still have been able to grab one. At the moment, we are focusing our production capacity, so small-batch S1 retail is not the top priority. If you have a clear batch demand later, we can absolutely keep talking about the S1.","literal_zh":"S1 是我们的旗舰系列，性能和配置更高，但成本也更高。之前还有少量零售库存，如果你们早几天来，可能还能买到。现在我们更倾向于集中产能，不太优先支持 S1 的小批量零售。如果后面你们有明确的批量需求，S1 也可以继续沟通。","audio":null},{"id":31,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Product Versions, Pricing, and Delivery Schedule","section_zh":"六、产品版本、价格与交付排期","english":"The T1 is the mass-production product we are pushing the hardest right now. It actually came out last October, and batch delivery started this year. Because it is more affordable than the S1, demand has been really strong, so the delivery schedule is tight. If you place an order now, delivery may land around late August or early September. If it is truly urgent, I can try to coordinate internally and see whether one unit from a batch order can go to you first, but I cannot fully promise that.","literal_zh":"T1 是现在重点推进的量产产品。T1 其实去年十月就已经出来了，今年开始批量交付。因为价格相对 S1 更低，客户需求比较多，所以目前排期比较紧。如果现在下单，可能要排到八月底或九月初才能交付。如果确实紧急，我们可以尝试和同事协调，看批量订单里有没有机器能先交给你们，但这个不能完全保证。","audio":null},{"id":32,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Product Versions, Pricing, and Delivery Schedule","section_zh":"六、产品版本、价格与交付排期","english":"For pricing, we have several versions. The half-body version is around RMB 89,900, and it is mainly for lighter desktop scenarios, like vending or popcorn demos, but it does not include full interfaces. The basic full-body version is around RMB 149,900, and that usually includes one robot and one remote controller, but no secondary development and no API access. The T1 secondary-development version is around RMB 315,270 including tax, and if we go by the public single-unit retail price, it may be higher.","literal_zh":"关于价格，现场有几个版本。半身版大概是 8.99 万元，主要适合桌面售卖、爆米花这类轻量场景，不含完整接口。基础全身版大概 14.99 万元，通常是一台机器人加一个遥控手柄，不含二开能力，也没有 API 接口。T1 二开版含税价格大概是 31.527 万元。如果按公开零售单台口径，价格可能更高。","audio":null},{"id":33,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Product Versions, Pricing, and Delivery Schedule","section_zh":"六、产品版本、价格与交付排期","english":"The exact price depends on the configuration, so this is where we need to match the setup to your real use case. Options like the universal adapter board, automatic charging station, extra computing power, upgraded vision, and depth cameras will all change the final number. If you can first clarify your budget and requirements, I can help you put together a configuration that actually makes sense. The final price can be discussed, but only if you are seriously planning to buy. Feature access and interfaces are all negotiable.","literal_zh":"具体价格还是要看配置。比如万能转接板、自动充电站、额外算力、高配视觉、深度相机等选项，都会影响最终价格。你们要先明确预算和需求，我再帮你们做配置搭配。最终价格可以谈，但前提是你们确实要买。功能开放和接口这些都好谈。","audio":null},{"id":34,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Product Versions, Pricing, and Delivery Schedule","section_zh":"六、产品版本、价格与交付排期","english":"The T1 is really popular right now. Today I can say August delivery might still be possible, but tomorrow I may not be able to say the same thing because we have our weekly meeting on Monday. Right now, the deposit is only RMB 10,000, and I also need to coordinate with the model team. Honestly, for a robot in the two-hundred-thousand-yuan range, the value is pretty solid.","literal_zh":"T1 现在确实很抢手。我今天可以说八月份有可能出货，但明天可能就不能保证，因为周一要开周会。现在只需要一万块钱定金。我还要和模型团队沟通。实话说，一台机器人二十来万，这个价格确实还算划算。","audio":null},{"id":35,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Compute, Vision, Battery, and Interface Configuration","section_zh":"七、算力、视觉、电池与接口配置","english":"The robot uses body-side edge computing plus host-machine computing. The S1 uses Orange Pi, and the T1 mainly uses RK3588. Think of the edge computer as the robot's input-output and relay hub: it handles images, sensors, control commands, data access, and forwarding, and it also does some local computing. For heavier model inference, you can run that on the host machine or on external computing hardware.","literal_zh":"机器人采用的是“本体边缘计算 + 上位机算力”的架构。S1 用的是 Orange Pi，T1 主要用 RK3588。边缘计算平台更像输入输出和中继节点，负责图像、传感器、控制指令等数据的接入和转发，也承担部分本地计算。更重的模型推理，可以放在上位机或外部算力设备上。","audio":null},{"id":36,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Compute, Vision, Battery, and Interface Configuration","section_zh":"七、算力、视觉、电池与接口配置","english":"Inside the company, we talk about the model capability as something like a big brain and a small brain. The small brain is closer to the execution layer: routine task reasoning, action assignment, and safety control. The big brain is more about complex task planning and higher-level decisions. If you buy our robot now, the small-brain system comes with it.","literal_zh":"我们内部把模型能力分成类似“大脑”和“小脑”的层级。“小脑”更偏执行层，负责常规任务的推理、动作分配和安全控制；“大脑”更偏复杂任务规划和高层决策。现在买我们的机器人，会一起交付小脑系统。","audio":null},{"id":37,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Compute, Vision, Battery, and Interface Configuration","section_zh":"七、算力、视觉、电池与接口配置","english":"For vision, the T1 is slightly reduced compared with the S1. For example, the head camera and chest camera setups are different. Depth cameras, head vision, and automatic charging stations can all be selected based on what the customer needs. If you already have your own computing platform, you can choose a lower-compute version and connect your own high-performance GPU or external computing device.","literal_zh":"视觉配置方面，T1 相比 S1 有一定减配，比如头部摄像头和胸部摄像头配置不一样。深度相机、头部视觉、自动充电站等模块可以按客户需求选配。如果你们有自己的算力平台，也可以选择低配算力版本，再自己接高性能显卡或外部计算设备。","audio":null},{"id":38,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Compute, Vision, Battery, and Interface Configuration","section_zh":"七、算力、视觉、电池与接口配置","english":"For battery life, the S1 is rated at about five to six hours, and the T1 is rated at about two to three hours. The T1 supports battery replacement, which gives you more flexibility during longer sessions. Actual battery life will still depend on load, task intensity, and the exact configuration.","literal_zh":"电池方面，S1 标称续航大概五到六小时，T1 标称续航大概两到三小时。T1 支持更换电池。实际续航会受负载、任务强度和具体配置影响。","audio":null},{"id":39,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Compute, Vision, Battery, and Interface Configuration","section_zh":"七、算力、视觉、电池与接口配置","english":"The T1 can be configured with a universal adapter board, which is basically what lets it connect to different hands, grippers, navigation peripherals, and other external devices. The T1 and S1 are similar in hollow wiring, force drive, and transmission structure, but the T1 reduces arm length, body structure, and some configurations. That keeps the cost under control and makes it much better suited for mass production.","literal_zh":"T1 可以配置万能转接板，用来对接灵巧手、夹爪、导航外设等不同末端或外设。T1 和 S1 在中空走线、力的驱动和传输结构上有相似之处，但 T1 在手臂长度、构型和部分配置上做了缩减，这样可以控制成本，也更适合量产。","audio":null},{"id":40,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Compute, Vision, Battery, and Interface Configuration","section_zh":"七、算力、视觉、电池与接口配置","english":"The T1 currently supports secondary development, and the secondary-development version opens API access. If you want to build a production line, whether for data collection or actual production, you will need drivers and control programs on the RK3588. You also need a stable control link between the robot body and the host machine, because that link is what keeps the whole workflow reliable.","literal_zh":"目前 T1 支持二次开发，二开版会开放 API 接口。你们如果要装一条产线，无论是做数采还是实际生产，都需要在 RK3588 上做驱动和控制程序，也需要在机器人本体和上位机之间建立稳定的控制链路。","audio":null},{"id":41,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Operating System and Secondary Development","section_zh":"八、操作系统与二次开发","english":"If you want to build a robot operating system, I actually think that fits really well with our underlying logic. In the future, robots may work more like computers or phones: hardware body first, then an operating system, and then an app ecosystem on top. When users need a function, they download the matching app. For example, a cooking app could let the robot handle certain cooking tasks, and a navigation or shopping app could help it take on more complex outside tasks.","literal_zh":"你们如果想做机器人操作系统，我觉得和我们的底层逻辑是比较一致的。未来机器人可能会像电脑或手机一样，形成“硬件本体 + 操作系统 + 应用生态”的模式。用户需要什么功能，就下载对应应用。比如下载炒菜应用，机器人就能完成某类烹饪任务；下载导航或采购应用，机器人就可以执行更复杂的外部任务。","audio":null},{"id":42,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Operating System and Secondary Development","section_zh":"八、操作系统与二次开发","english":"I think ROS1 and ROS2 are great for R&D and low-level development, but they are not the final user experience for everyday people. A consumer-facing robot system should feel much simpler, more like using phone apps. Users should not have to understand the underlying technology; they should just pick what they want the robot to do, and the system should handle the rest.","literal_zh":"我觉得 ROS1 和 ROS2 更适合作为研发和底层开发框架，不是真正面向大众用户的最终产品形态。面向 C 端用户的系统应该更简单，就像手机应用一样，用户不需要理解底层技术，只需要选择功能。","audio":null},{"id":43,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Operating System and Secondary Development","section_zh":"八、操作系统与二次开发","english":"The T1 system architecture has some compatibility. If you need ROS2, we can help flash it in or do the adaptation work. Right now, the T1 uses Xingchen's own operating system, and my understanding is that it is packaged and improved on top of a ROS-like base. The system can keep evolving into V2, V3, and beyond.","literal_zh":"T1 的系统架构有一定兼容性。如果你们需要 ROS2，我们可以协助刷进去或做适配。现在 T1 用的是星尘自己的操作系统，我理解它是在 ROS 类底座上做了进一步封装和改良。后续系统也可以继续迭代到 V2、V3。","audio":null},{"id":44,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Operating System and Secondary Development","section_zh":"八、操作系统与二次开发","english":"In the future, robots will definitely call different capabilities based on user instructions. The computing demand is huge, and it is not realistic for every home to have its own server sitting there. So future robots may need remote computing support. Computing power may be charged, and different apps may be charged too. Whether that becomes a monthly subscription or a one-time purchase depends on how the whole app ecosystem is designed.","literal_zh":"机器人以后一定会根据指令调用不同能力。因为算力需求很大，每个家庭不可能都配一台服务器，所以未来可能需要远程算力支撑。算力会收费，各种应用也会收费。具体是按月收费，还是一次性购买，要看整个 App 生态怎么设计。","audio":null},{"id":45,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Operating System and Secondary Development","section_zh":"八、操作系统与二次开发","english":"Right now, we still do not have enough data; in a year, we may only collect around 50,000 hours. But once a lot of robots are collecting data at the same time, the scale will eventually get there. It could be 100 million hours, or even 1 billion hours.","literal_zh":"现在数据还不够，一年也只有五万个小时。但以后可以通过大量机器人采集，数据总会达到相应量级，无论是一亿小时还是十亿小时。","audio":null},{"id":46,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"In industrial scenarios, grippers can already cover a lot of tasks. But in the long run, end effectors will probably move more toward dexterous hands, because dexterous hands are much closer to human hands and are better for complex, general-purpose tasks.","literal_zh":"工业场景中，夹爪可以覆盖很多任务。但从长期看，机器人末端形态可能还是会逐渐向灵巧手收敛，因为灵巧手更接近人手，适合更复杂、更泛化的任务。","audio":null},{"id":47,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"That said, dexterous hands also have durability challenges. If customers run them at high intensity for a long time, they wear faster, so dexterous-hand manufacturers still need to keep improving that part. Right now, we have high-degree-of-freedom solutions with twenty degrees of freedom, and we also have simpler options like six-degree-of-freedom hands.","literal_zh":"不过，灵巧手也有耐久性问题。如果客户让灵巧手长期高强度工作，磨损会比较快，这部分需要灵巧手厂家继续提升。我们现在有二十自由度的高自由度方案，也有六自由度这类更简化的方案。","audio":null},{"id":48,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"For force control, the robot is not just doing open and close like a simple clamp. It can control how much force it applies. For example, when it holds a glass cup, the software can limit the maximum force so the robot does not crush it. That kind of control is very important for desktop tasks, retail, food service, and service scenarios.","literal_zh":"力控方面，机器人不是只有“开”和“合”两种状态，而是可以控制夹持力度。比如夹玻璃杯时，可以通过软件限制最大力，避免夹碎物体。这类能力对于桌面操作、零售、餐饮和服务场景都很重要。","audio":null},{"id":49,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"The scenarios we work with most include homes, commercial displays, culture and tourism, retail, and some industrial applications. Home and commercial scenarios show up more often, while industrial scenarios are fewer because they almost always need adaptation. Every factory has its own production lines, tooling, and workflow, so you cannot just copy and paste one solution everywhere.","literal_zh":"目前我们接触和落地比较多的场景，包括家庭、商业展示、文旅、零售和部分工业应用。家庭和商业场景相对更多，工业场景会少一些，因为工业场景都需要适配。不同工厂的产线、工装和流程差异很大，不能简单复制。","audio":null},{"id":50,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"In industrial scenarios, customers may need custom fixtures, tooling, or even a full end-to-end workflow. Even for the same type of factory, the process may differ by region or by production line. So robot applications usually need to be adapted around the exact step where the robot will be used.","literal_zh":"工业场景里，客户可能需要定制夹具、工装或端到端流程。即使是同一类工厂，不同地区或不同产线的工艺流程也可能不同，所以机器人应用往往要按具体环节重新适配。","audio":null},{"id":51,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"We already have customers using the robots in real production, including Xianfeng Lingyu and Jinma Rides. We have a data-collection factory in Guizhou and another one in Ma'anshan, and there are also more than one hundred units in Linyi. We also cooperate with Pai on large models. I do not know the exact details, but I do know the cooperation is real.","literal_zh":"我们目前已经实际应用到生产里的客户，包括先锋领域、金马游乐等。贵州有一个数采厂，马鞍山也有一个数采厂。临沂那边也有一百多台。我们和“派”在大模型方面有合作，但具体合作内容我不太清楚，只知道确实有合作。","audio":null},{"id":52,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"End Effectors and Application Scenarios","section_zh":"九、末端执行器与应用场景","english":"Culture, tourism, and display scenarios also have demand. Some customers buy robots for clubs, showrooms, or stage displays, and they use remote control to create interactive movements. These customers may not need the full secondary-development package; they care more about the look, the interaction, and whether the demo feels impressive in person.","literal_zh":"文旅和展示场景也有需求。有些客户买机器人就是用来做会所、展厅或舞台展示，通过遥控完成互动动作。这类客户不一定需要完整二开能力，更看重外观、互动和演示效果。","audio":null},{"id":53,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"After-Sales, Certifications, and Overseas Compliance","section_zh":"十、售后、认证与海外合规","english":"For after-sales service, if the robot breaks, it can be shipped back for repair. If it is still under warranty, we cover the related shipping costs, and the warranty period is one year. Honestly, after-sales agreements are pretty similar across companies, but shipping a robot this size back and forth is definitely inconvenient. So for some issues, we can also send people on site, depending on what kind of problem it is.","literal_zh":"售后方面，如果机器人坏了，可以寄回来维修。如果在保修期内，我们承担相关运费，保修期是一年。售后协议其实各家都差不多。不过这么大一台机器来回寄确实麻烦，所以有些问题我们也可以派人到现场处理，具体要看问题类型。","audio":null},{"id":54,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"After-Sales, Certifications, and Overseas Compliance","section_zh":"十、售后、认证与海外合规","english":"Many after-sales issues can be solved through online guidance, especially configuration, interface, or operation problems. For customers in other cities, whether we ask them to ship the robot back or send someone on site depends on how complex the issue is.","literal_zh":"很多售后问题可以通过线上指导解决，比如配置、接口或操作问题。对于异地客户，到底是寄修还是上门，要看问题复杂度。","audio":null},{"id":55,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"After-Sales, Certifications, and Overseas Compliance","section_zh":"十、售后、认证与海外合规","english":"For overseas markets, we have not fully built out an overseas after-sales system yet. A French customer previously bought an S1 to replace part of a production process in his factory. We delivered the robot in China, and then he arranged his own freight forwarder to ship it overseas. Because overseas certification and compliance are not fully completed yet, overseas pricing and delivery methods will be different from domestic ones.","literal_zh":"海外方面，我们目前还没有完全建立海外售后体系。之前有一个法国客户买了一台 S1，用来替代工厂里的部分生产环节。他是在国内交货，然后自己找货代运出去。因为海外认证和合规流程还没有完全完成，所以海外售价和交付方式会和国内不同。","audio":null},{"id":56,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"After-Sales, Certifications, and Overseas Compliance","section_zh":"十、售后、认证与海外合规","english":"For certifications, the full robot has not completed explosion-proof, dust-proof, or water-proof certification yet. For key components like batteries, we require compliance certificates when purchasing them, but that does not mean the whole robot has completed every industrial certification. So if the robot is going into factories, chemical sites, outdoor environments, or other high-protection scenarios, we need to confirm the certification requirements case by case.","literal_zh":"认证方面，目前整机还没有完成防爆、防尘、防水认证。电池等关键部件采购时会要求合格证明，但这不等于整机已经完成全部工业认证。所以如果进入工厂、化工、户外或高防护等级场景，还需要进一步确认认证要求。","audio":null},{"id":57,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"After-Sales, Certifications, and Overseas Compliance","section_zh":"十、售后、认证与海外合规","english":"Overseas data compliance is actually a lot like phones going global. The key issues are privacy and data compliance. Directly exporting domestic data to Europe or the U.S. can create compliance risk, but trained skills, model capabilities, or app capabilities can still be exported in a compliant way.","literal_zh":"出海的数据合规问题，和手机出海很像。核心问题是隐私和数据合规。国内数据直接出口到欧美地区会有合规风险，但已经训练好的技能、模型能力或应用能力，可以通过合规方式输出。","audio":null},{"id":58,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"After-Sales, Certifications, and Overseas Compliance","section_zh":"十、售后、认证与海外合规","english":"For example, if I buy a robot and send it to the U.S. to cook three dishes, what I really need is not the raw data; what I need is the trained skill. The premise is that the robot's generalization and autonomy are already good enough to use, so it does not need to collect a huge amount of extra data. Of course, by that stage, the robot may still collect some data, but it can be processed locally through U.S. servers or U.S.-based cloud services. Phones work in a similar way, and Apple's data center in Guizhou was also about meeting compliance requirements.","literal_zh":"比如我买了一台机器人，让它去美国炒三道菜，我需要的不是原始数据，而是已经训练好的技能。这里的前提是，机器人的泛化能力和自主能力已经达到可用程度，不需要再额外收集大量数据。当然，到那个阶段，机器人可能仍然会收集一部分数据，但可以在美国部署服务器或购买云服务，在美国本地处理。手机也是类似逻辑，苹果在贵州设数据中心，也是为了解决合规问题。","audio":null},{"id":59,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Future Cooperation and Shenzhen Supply-Chain Advantage","section_zh":"十一、后续合作与深圳供应链优势","english":"If you want to build a robot operating system or a robot app ecosystem in the future, our robot could be one of the hardware bases. That direction actually matches our thinking pretty well: hardware body, operating system, and app ecosystem.","literal_zh":"如果你们未来想做机器人操作系统或机器人应用生态，我觉得我们家的机器人可以作为硬件底座之一。我们在“硬件本体 + 操作系统 + 应用生态”这个方向上的思路比较接近。","audio":null},{"id":60,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Future Cooperation and Shenzhen Supply-Chain Advantage","section_zh":"十一、后续合作与深圳供应链优势","english":"In the short term, if you only buy one or two robots, it probably will not pull in a lot of R&D resources from our company. But if we confirm product fit and define a clearer cooperation direction, I can help push things forward internally. That means bringing in our R&D team, model team, and after-sales team so we can have a deeper conversation with you.","literal_zh":"短期内，如果你们只采购一两台机器人，可能不会撬动公司太多研发资源。但如果确认产品适配，并且形成更明确的合作方向，我可以推动公司研发、模型、售后等团队和你们做更深入的交流。","audio":null},{"id":61,"speaker":"Xingchen","section":"Future Cooperation and Shenzhen Supply-Chain Advantage","section_zh":"十一、后续合作与深圳供应链优势","english":"I think your team will probably set up a team in Shenzhen later, and the reason is simple. Shenzhen has lower manufacturing costs and an incredibly dense supply chain. Within a ten-kilometer radius, you can source a huge share of the parts needed to build a robot, and that is hard for Shanghai, Hangzhou, or Beijing to match. For robot hardware development and fast iteration, Shenzhen is just a better place to get things built quickly.","literal_zh":"我觉得你们团队后面大概率也会在深圳成立团队。原因很简单：深圳制造成本低，供应链密度高。方圆十公里内，做一台机器人所需的大量零部件基本都能配齐。上海、杭州、北京很难做到这一点。对于机器人硬件开发和快速迭代来说，深圳的供应链环境更适合落地。","audio":null}]};
